    "明天一大早啊。{p}嗯……能起得来吧？{p}今晚先尽早把东西准备利索比较好。"

# game/day 7.rpy:199
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_2dfd8a2b:

    # who "「Good evening, is this the [ln] residence?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 279)
    who "「喂，这里是[西村]君的家吗？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:200
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_9066b454:

    # fn "「Yes, it is...{p} Is that you, Shun-kun?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 282)
    fn "「嗯，是的……{w=.3}你是峻君吗？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:201
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_fd6a48bf:

    # su "「Yes! This is Shun!{p} [fn]-san, good evening.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 285)
    su "「是的！{w=.3}　我是峻！{w=.3}　[fn]君你好啊♪」"

# game/day 7.rpy:202
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_e20a1f86:

    # fn "「Good evening to you too, what's up?{p} Is there something you need?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 288)
    fn "「你好。怎么了？{w=.3}　找我有事吗？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:203
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_dda1993b:

    # su "「Yes there is!{p} The other day at the welcoming party,{p} we were talking about going to the beach.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 291-292)
    su "「是的！{w=.3}　嗯…前些天的欢迎会上，{p}说过去海水浴这样的话吧」"

# game/day 7.rpy:204
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_18467e8f:

    # fn "「Oh yeah, we did!{p} Have we decided on a plan?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 303-304)
    fn "「嗯嗯，确实是呢！{p}定好计划了吗？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:205
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_c238025e:

    # su "「Umm, err...{p} Tomorrow, but if that's...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 307-308)
    su "「呃，那个…{p}明，明天……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:206
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_59569605:

    # "He murmurs an apology in a low voice.{p}Then he tells me they're planning,{p}on going in less than half a day."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 310-311)
    "轻声低语带着些许歉意。{p}距离峻君说出来的预定时间剩不到半天。"

# game/day 7.rpy:207
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_5aae7c4f:

    # "I'm surprised."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 312)
    "我，着实吃了一惊。"

# game/day 7.rpy:208
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_4a434ba5:

    # fn "「Huh!?{p} Tomorrow!? Tomorrow as in the 7th!?{p} The tomorrow that will come if I go to sleep?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 315-317)
    fn "「哈？！{p}明天！？{w=.3}　也就是说７号！？{p}睡一觉起来后的明天吧？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:209
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_963e0130:

    # su "「Yeah...{p} it's hard to get everybody's schedules to match up,{p} so we talked about different times and decided that..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 320-322)
    su "「是的……大家都有事情做所以时间一直敲不定，{p}在讨论了很多东西之后就决定了{p}是明天……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:210
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_396d0a0a:

    # su "Tomorrow is best...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 322)
    su "「是明天……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:211
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_4c099f05:

    # su "「[fn]-san, will you please go...?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 325)
    su "「[fn]君，你能来吗……？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:212
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_90f78225:

    # "I'm not so fickle,{p}that I would turn down your earnest request,{p}Shun-kun."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 327)
    "峻君用着微弱的声音期盼着。"

# game/day 7.rpy:213
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_ae86cf75:

    # "Fufufu, don't worry.{p}This is my chance to be a big brother!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 328-329)
    "哼哼哼，不用担心啊。{p}哥哥我可是超级闲的啊！"

# game/day 7.rpy:214
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_e0e2e3b0:

    # fn "「Of course! That's fine!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 332)
    fn "「当然了！{w=.3}　没关系的！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:215
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_f23d53e4:

    # "I give my reply,{p}and I hear the sound of relief and joy.{p}on the other end of the line."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 337-338)
    "对于我的答复，{p}电话那一头传来非常高兴的回应。"

# game/day 7.rpy:216
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_fb0014f4:

    # su "「Woof! That's good... I'm happy,{p} everybody's going!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 341-342)
    su "「哇呼！{w=.3}　太好了……真高兴，{p}大家能一起出去玩。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:217
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_0593f0b7:

    # "Judging by his excited tone,{p}I'm sure his tail is wagging at full throttle."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 344-345)
    "完全能看见峻君快乐的样子，{p}尾巴一定也是拼命的摇晃着吧。"

# game/day 7.rpy:218
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_761b0764:

    # "Fufufu, I love making him worry at first,{p}and then making him happy!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 346)
    "呵呵呵，稍微戏弄一下别人可是自己的强项啊！"

# game/day 7.rpy:219
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_6c00c67c:

    # fn "「Yeah, I'm going because it's been so long.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 352)
    fn "「是啊，真的是相隔很久了呢。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:220
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_53e1e801:

    # su "「The time and place we're meeting is... umm...{p} 7 in the morning at the bus stop.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 355)
    su "「时间和地点是……呃…早上７点在巴士站集合」"

# game/day 7.rpy:221
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_de88613b:

    # fn "「Mm-hm.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 358)
    fn "「嗯嗯」"

# game/day 7.rpy:222
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_ee456da6:

    # su "「You should bring your bathing suit,\n and stuff to play with.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 361)
    su "「要带的东西……有泳衣，还有玩的东西。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:223
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_02b8adfc:

    # fn "「I see. It feels like\n you've been putting a lot of effort\n into planning everything out!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 364-365)
    fn "「原来如此。就这样子顺便一起决定要带的东西对吧！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:224
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_724c3b3a:

    # su "「S-sorry...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 368)
    su "「对、对不起……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:225
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_ca63b679:

    # fn "「There's no need to apologize!{p} This is a little exciting!{p} It's like we're kids again, isn't it?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 371-372)
    fn "「不用道歉啦，不知怎么的有种兴奋的感觉呢，{p}就像回到小孩子的时候那样。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:226
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_86ce93fe:

    # su "「Th-that's right.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 375)
    su "「就、就是说啊！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:227
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_b89e50ab:

    # fn "「All right then,\n we're meeting at the bus stop tomorrow at 7.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 378)
    fn "「那么，明天７点在巴士站再见啦！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:228
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_697c64c7:

    # su "「Yes!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 381)
    su "「好的！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:229
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_5642f3ef:

    # "He methodically reapeat the time,\nmeeting spot, and what I need to bring."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 383)
    "做事仔细的峻君又再一次复述了时间、地点、要带的东西，"

# game/day 7.rpy:230
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shun_09be79b0:

    # "Excited and in high spirits,\nShun-kun hangs up the phone.{p}Well, I better start packing."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 384-385)
    "说了一句「真的很期待」，之后才挂上电话。{p}好啦，来准备行李吧。"

# game/day 7.rpy:239
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_kouya_04920635:

    # ka "「Yo, [fn]. It's me.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 400)
    ka "「哦，[fn]。是我」"

# game/day 7.rpy:240
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_kouya_284843c4:

    # fn "「Huh, Kouya? What are you calling for?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 402-403)
    fn "「啊咧，洸哉？{p}　打电话过来有什么事吗」"

# game/day 7.rpy:241
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_kouya_fef481cf:

    # ka "「Well, back at your welcoming party,\n everybody was talking about going to the beach...{p} You remember?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 406-408)
    ka "「没什么，之前在你的欢迎会上。{p}那时候大家说了要到海边{w=.3}之类的话，还记得吗？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:242
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_kouya_8212e223:

    # "I try to remember what we talked about.{p}Yeah, we did discuss that."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 410-411)
    "试着回忆了一下当时的情况。{p}那时候确实是做了那样的讨论。"

# game/day 7.rpy:243
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_kouya_0bb307aa:

    # fn "「Oh yeah, I remember.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 414)
    fn "「啊、还记得呢」"

# game/day 7.rpy:244
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_kouya_a835f94a:

    # ka "「About that, sorry if it's on such short notice...{p} But would tomorrow be okay?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 417)
    ka "「那个嘛，虽然通知得急有点抱歉……{p}明天的话不要紧吧？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:245
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_kouya_d937eb27:

    # "An apologetic voice comes from the phone."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 419)
    "略带歉意的声音从电话中传达出来。"

# game/day 7.rpy:246
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_kouya_6f708976:

    # fn "「Tomorrow?{p} Well, that should be all right,\n but why tomorrow?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 421-423)
    fn "「明天？{p}……没、不是很要紧，{w=.3}为什么选在明天呢？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:247
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_kouya_d5a8f9a2:

    # ka "「Ah, if you think about everybody's plans,\n then this is when it's most convenient.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 426-427)
    ka "「啊，考虑到大家的社团活动什么的，{w=.3}刚好明天都有空而已。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:248
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_kouya_265f1022:

    # ka "「If we miss tomorrow, I don't know\n when the next time could be,{p} so we have to do it then.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 430-431)
    ka "「如果明天不去的话下一次不知道要到什么时间了，{w=.3}所以就决定是明天去了。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:249
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_kouya_893f3074:

    # fn "「Oh, I see.{p} Yeah, sounds good.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 433-435)
    fn "「啊，原来如此。{p}嗯，我明白了。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:250
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_kouya_78584994:

    # ka "「I'm really sorry for being so sudden.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 438)
    ka "「真对不起，这么仓促」"

# game/day 7.rpy:251
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_kouya_91b94b82:

    # fn "「No, you don't need to apologize.{p} Have you decided on a meeting time?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 441-442)
    fn "「没事，洸哉不用道歉。{p}什么时候集合？已经决定好了吗？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:252
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_kouya_ff03cd1c:

    # ka "「Uh, tomorrow morning at seven.\n we're meeting at the bus stop.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 445)
    ka "「啊、打算明早７点在巴士站集合。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:253
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_kouya_e93ba5e7:

    # ka "「There's nothing specific that you need,{p} so bring whatever you want.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 446-447)
    ka "「也没有什么东西需要特别准备的，{w=.3}行李就随你喜欢好了。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:254
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_kouya_da1afb96:

    # fn "「Yeah, got it.{p} I'll see you tomorrow.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 450-451)
    fn "「嗯、知道了。{p}那明天见」"

# game/day 7.rpy:255
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_kouya_bdc8c3d0:

    # ka "「Yeah, see ya.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 454)
    ka "「哦，那再见啊」"

# game/day 7.rpy:256
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_kouya_357d512c:

    # "*Click*{p}I hang up the phone."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 456)
    "咔嚓一声，我挂掉了电话。"

# game/day 7.rpy:257
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_kouya_ec182b6e:

    # "So, it's tomorrow.{p}Even though it was so sudden,\nI'm somehow already excited."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 458-459)
    "是吗、明天啊。{p}说起来是十分突然啦，不过还是很让人期待的。"

# game/day 7.rpy:258
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_kouya_874937c5:

    # "Okay, I have to start preparing right away."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 460)
    "好，快点准备吧。"

# game/day 7.rpy:267
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_juuichi_f2e9ec1b:

    # ju "「Hello, this is Mikazuki speaking.{p} Is [fn]-kun home?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 468-469)
    ju "「喂，您好。{p}我是三日月，{w=.3}请问[fn]君在家吗？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:268
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_juuichi_599366b3:

    # "I hear Juuichi-san's voice from the phone.{p}His tone seems somewhat higher than usual."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 471-472)
    "从电话中听到的是柔一的声音。{p}不知是否是我多心，{w=.3}总觉得他的声音比平常要高了些。"

# game/day 7.rpy:269
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_juuichi_9f18b2d5:

    # fn "「Oh, Juuichi-san, this is [fn].{p} Good evening.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 474-475)
    fn "「啊，{w=.3}柔一，是我啦。{w=.3}晚安。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:270
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_juuichi_05a371e5:

    # "Juuichi-san always uses honorifics\nwhen speaking to me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 477-478)
    "平常都是我在对柔一说敬语，{w=.3}像这样听到柔一用如此慎重的语气讲话感觉真微妙。"

# game/day 7.rpy:271
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_juuichi_c8fb8969:

    # "His respectful way of talking\nis kind of embarrassing."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 478-479)
    "这种对谁都如此有礼貌的说话方式，{p}真让人难为情。"

# game/day 7.rpy:272
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_juuichi_28efb15e:

    # "While I'm thinking about that,{p}Juuichi-san greets me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 479)
    "我一边这么想着，一边隔着电话跟他打招呼。"

# game/day 7.rpy:273
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_juuichi_bfd787ab:

    # ju "「...[ln].{p} I'm sorry for calling at a time like this.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 481-482)
    ju "「……[西村]吗。{p}抱歉啦，{w=.3}这种时间还打电话。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:274
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_juuichi_43b1816f:

    # fn "「No no, that's all right.{p} What do you need?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 484-486)
    fn "「不会不会，{w=.3}没关系的。{p}那今天是有什么事吗？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:275
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_juuichi_3e1e6601:

    # ju "「Ahem...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 488-489)
    ju "「啊啊。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:276
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_juuichi_f2a1e797:

    # "Juuichi-san lightly clears his throat."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 491)
    "柔一轻轻地咳了一下。"

# game/day 7.rpy:277
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_juuichi_16fa3419:

    # ju "「A few days ago, at your welcoming party,\n do you remember talking about going to the beach?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 493-495)
    ju "「之前在欢迎会上，{w=.3}有聊到要去海边玩的事，你还记得吗？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:278
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_juuichi_9a1e26f5:

    # fn "「I remember.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 498)
    fn "「这我当然记得喽。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:279
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_juuichi_32d5decf:

    # ju "「Well, we were planning on going, but...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 501-503)
    ju "「是吗，那这样讲起来就简单了。{w=.3}就是这件事。{p}高原在确认了大家的行程，整理了一下后，{w=.3}终于决定要哪一天去海边了……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:280
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_juuichi_874f7771:

    # fn "「Is that right? Sounds fun.{p} ...When are you going?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 513-515)
    fn "「是这样啊。{p}那，{w=.3}是要什么时候去？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:281
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_juuichi_c4ed719e:

    # ju "「...Um. Tomorrow.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 517-518)
    ju "「……嗯。{w=.3}是明天。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:282
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_juuichi_e964b5f1:

    # fn "「All right, tomorrow it is.{p} ...{p} Tomorrow!?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 520-521)
    fn "「好好，{w=.3}是明天吗。{p}……明天！？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:283
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_juuichi_1a7ba095:

    # "I accidently yelled that out loud.{p}Going to the beach would be fun,\nbut isn't that kind of soon?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 523-525)
