# game/day 7.rpy:284
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_juuichi_51a22b24:

    # ju "「...Sorry. Tomorrow is the only time\n everybody will be able to go.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 527-529)
    ju "「……抱歉。{w=.3}为了配合大家的状况，{p}最后只剩下明天可以了。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:285
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_juuichi_64930d9c:

    # "Juuichi-san's tone is apologetic.{p}That's right, they have their club activites,\nsupplementary lessons, and other stuff."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 531-532)
    "柔一用很不好意思的语气说着。{p}是吗，{w=.3}说起来大家也是要社团活动和补习什么的。"

# game/day 7.rpy:286
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_juuichi_e556b0c3:

    # "Tomorrow...{p}I don't have anything important to do,\nso I readily agree."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 540-542)
    "明天……{p}我也没有什么特别的安排，{p}于是马上就答应了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:287
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_juuichi_55db55d4:

    # ju "「I see.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 544-545)
    ju "「是吗，{w=.3}这么突然真不好意思，不过就请你准备了。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:288
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_juuichi_e755f39c:

    # "It could be my imagination,\nbut Juuichi-san's voice sounds more lively."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 588)
