# game/day 7.rpy:330
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_shin_c1ce6a55:

    # si "「Never mind.{p} Anyway, there's not much you need to do to prepare.{p} Tomorrow morning at 7, meet at the bus stop. Okay?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 702-704)
