# game/day 7.rpy:365
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_soutarou_24bf99c0:

    # fn "「Got it. Thanks for telling me.{p} Soutarou-kun, make sure to get plenty of sleep, okay?」"
    # [机翻] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 791-792)
    fn "「知道了。特意来告诉我，谢谢。{p}宗太郎君，今晚要好好睡觉哦？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:366
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_soutarou_fe3d3a32:

    # so "「Th...thank you very much!{p} Now, if you'll excuse me! G'night」"
    # [机翻] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 795-796)
    so "「啊……非常感谢！{p}那么，我就先告辞了！晚安」"

# game/day 7.rpy:367
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_soutarou_ec992762:

    # fn "「Yeah. Good night.」"
    # [机翻] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 799)
    fn "「嗯。晚安——」"

# game/day 7.rpy:368
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_soutarou_7f42b7da:

    # "Finished talking, I hang up the phone."
    # [机翻] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 801)
    "我把电话放好了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:369
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_soutarou_439c1099:

    # fn "「Before going on a field trip...」"
    # [机翻] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 804)
    fn "「去远足之前，吗……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:370
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_soutarou_2e0e17b9:

    # "When I hear field trip, I suddenly remember,{p}when I used to live in this village."
    # [机翻] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 806)
    "听到远足这个词，不禁想起了在这个村子时的自己。"

# game/day 7.rpy:371
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_soutarou_bd8d543d:

    # "I haven't gone on a trip like this,{p}with everybody since elementary school."
    # [机翻] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 807)
    "像这样和大家一起远行还是小学以来第一次呢。"

# game/day 7.rpy:372
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_soutarou_6fe2292b:

    # fn "「...Okay! Let's finish preparing for tomorrow.」"
    # [机翻] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 810)
    fn "「……好！来把明天的准备做完吧」"

# game/day 7.rpy:373
translate chinese_simplified beach07_invite_soutarou_909969f3:

    # "I quickly get back to my room."
    # [机翻] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 812)
    "我快步走回了自己的房间。"

# game/day 7.rpy:386
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_dce31dbc:

    # "Let's see...{p}We're probably going swimming,\nso I'll bring my swim trunks, and my sandals."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 832-834)
    "那个……。{p}既然去游泳的话，带上泳裤就好了吧，\\n还有拖鞋来的。"

# game/day 7.rpy:387
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_bc8a4560:

    # "Oh, I don't have goggles...{p}But they sell those at the 100 yen shop.\nI'll just buy them there."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 836-838)
    "啊，没有泳镜……。{p}不过，百元商店应该有卖的，\\n等到了之后再买吧。"

# game/day 7.rpy:388
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_3550fb39:

    # "I wonder if I should get a swim ring,\nor something like that..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 840)
    "泳圈要怎么办好呢？"

# game/day 7.rpy:392
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_02a69938:

    # fn "「Grandma, I'm going to the beach tomorrow.{p} Do we have like a beach ball or something?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 844-845)
    fn "「奶奶，明天要去海边，{p}家里有没有泳圈呢？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:393
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_7717b10b:

    # gm "「I wonder where it is...{p} If I remember correctly,\n your father had one.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 848-850)
    gm "「啊，好像是放在什么地方了……{p}以前你爸爸确实有用过的，\\n放在哪里了呢……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:394
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_2bc7e274:

    # gm "「At least, I think he had one...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 850)
    gm "「嗯，应该是有过的……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:395
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_05a4d585:

    # "If Dad did use one,\nit'll be from 10 or 20 years ago..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 852-853)
    "爸爸用过的……\\n那不是已经过了好几十年了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:396
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_59b58dc1:

    # fn "「Oh, you don't need to get it,\n I was just curious.\n I'm sure everybody else will have them.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 856-857)
    fn "「啊，不用找了，\\n只是问问而已。\\n大家手里应该会有多余的用。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:397
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_9606b486:

    # gm "「Are you sure?{p} Guess I don't have to get it out.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 860)
    gm "「是吗？{p}那不用拿出来了。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:398
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_acbd9957:

    # "Even if they don't have plenty,\nit'll be fine as long as somebody brings one..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 862-863)
    "就算大家没有多余的用，\\n反正只要有人带了去，就可以借用嘛……"

# game/day 7.rpy:399
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_c2a991d2:

    # fn "「Thank you, though.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 866)
    fn "「谢谢啦。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:400
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_16b7d049:

    # "Even if there's something I don't have,\nthey'll probably have it at the beach store."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 868)
    "其他东西的话，\\n在海之家那里就有卖的。"

# game/day 7.rpy:401
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_520bca04:

    # "So there, that's enough packing.{p}I need to get to bed early for tomorrow."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 869-870)
    "这样的话，已经准备完毕了。{p}为了明天，早些睡吧。"

# game/day 7.rpy:421
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_0d482e90:

    # "Huh... It's morning already?{p}What time is it?{p}5:53 AM..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 881-882)
    "啊咧……天亮了？{p}现在几点了？{p}5点53分……"

# game/day 7.rpy:422
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_2b265694:

    # "I set my alarm for 6,\nbut I got up earlier than that."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 884-885)
    "原打算是六点钟再起的，\\n好像起早了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:423
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_38fa776c:

    # "Why is it whenever I go on a trip,\nI always wake up early?{p}Strange..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 887-888)
    "为什么一到远足的日子，\\n就能成功地早睡早起呢？{p}不可思议。"

# game/day 7.rpy:424
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_4fbb9d0e:

    # fn "「Good morning.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 891)
    fn "「早啊——」"

# game/day 7.rpy:425
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_0401d746:

    # gm "「Good morning. I got up early myself.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 894)
    gm "「早。{p}自己就起来了呢。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:426
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_a37c33d9:

    # gp "「You're up early.{p} You're usually sleeping like a log at this hour.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 897-898)
    gp "「今天起得可真早啊，{p}平时这个时候都还在睡。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:427
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_2a32cd64:

    # "Old people sure do get up early...{p}I wonder if that means that I'm an old man..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 900-901)
    "上了年纪的人起得都好早啊……{p}等我到了爷爷这年纪，估计也能这么早起了吧。"

# game/day 7.rpy:428
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_14303d05:

    # gm "「Go wash your face.{p} I'll make you something to eat.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 904)
    gm "「去洗脸吧。{p}我准备早饭。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:429
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_c0b14b65:

    # fn "「Okay...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 907)
    fn "「好……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:430
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_fbfd4b89:

    # "Everybody else is probably still asleep."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 909)
    "大家应该还在睡吧。"

# game/day 7.rpy:431
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_8a887fcf:

    # fn "「Thanks for breakfast.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 912)
    fn "「我吃饱了。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:432
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_ee59ff59:

    # "Well, it's a little early,\nbut I'll go to the bus stop.{p}I can't wait anymore!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 45-47)
    "嗯，时间还早，\\n先去公交车站吧。{p}等不及了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:433
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_9ad1e57e:

    # fn "「All right, I'm leaving now.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 50)
    fn "「那么，我走了。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:434
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_29c92b5a:

    # gm "「Oh, heading out so soon?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 53)
    gm "「啊，现在就走？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:435
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_2c1b2868:

    # gp "「All right, be careful.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 56)
    gp "「哦哦，路上小心。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:436
translate chinese_simplified beach07_packing_9b75e8ea:

    # fn "「See you later.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 7日目.ks (KS 59)
    fn "「嗯，我出门了。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:449
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_1695ed5d:

    # "Early in the morning, I hurry to the bus stop.\nIt doesn't look like everybody's here yet..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 11-12)
    "正如我所预料到的，我还是提前到了。\n看来大家都还没到齐啊……"

# game/day 7.rpy:450
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_f70c1b0b:

    # fn "「That person over there...\n Is that...?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 16-20)
    fn "「那边那个是……\n看着好眼熟啊，莫非……？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:454
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_bfe45677:

    # ju "「...[ln].{p} You're here very early.{p} Isn't there plenty of time?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 23-25)
    ju "「……[西村]啊。{p}你到得真早。时间不还早么？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:455
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_67c0df4a:

    # fn "「Good morning.{p} I guess I woke up kind of early.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 27-29)
    fn "「早上好。{p}我觉得我的生物钟定得是有些早了。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:456
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_7ed6a8b5:

    # fn "「Besides, now you don't have to wait\n for me to get here.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 30)
    fn "「换句话说，这样你就不用在这等我来了吧。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:457
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_090dd1af:

    # fn "「You're early, too.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 33)
    fn "「你来得也够早啊。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:458
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_3d9a4d3a:

    # ju "「I get up early most days,\n since I have training.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 36)
    ju "「平常我起得很早的，因为我早上要训练。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:459
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_7513f417:

    # fn "「Heh, so you're an early riser.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 39)
    fn "「嘿，看来你是早起主义者。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:460
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_337ec6a6:

    # "Amazing."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 41)
    "真了不起啊。"

# game/day 7.rpy:461
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_269d6aad:

    # "If that's the case,\nKyouji and Torahiko probably have to get up\nearly for their clubs, too."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 42)
    "这样的话，京慈和宗太郎很可能也会早起去参加社团活动。"

# game/day 7.rpy:462
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_8cb84ed3:

    # "...Although waking up early doesn't suit Torahiko."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 43)
    "但是对于虎彦来说……早起是不太可能的。"

# game/day 7.rpy:463
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_8c896239:

    # fn "「By the way, Juuichi-san,\n it looks like you brought a lot of stuff.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 50-51)
    fn "「话说柔一，看起来你好像带了好多东西啊。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:464
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_8e20215c:

    # "I noticed it when I first saw him."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 53)
    "刚才我才注意到这个。"

# game/day 7.rpy:465
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_d0b2f23e:

    # "Juuichi-san has a backpack that's almost\nthe same size as his body.\nIt's stuffed full, and clinging to his back."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 55-56)
    "柔一君背着一个不小的背包，紧贴着他的身子。\n背包被塞满了，缓缓地从他的背上滑下。"

# game/day 7.rpy:466
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_a83ebd26:

    # "Do you think he'd say anything\nif I messed with it?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 58)
    "如果我拿来翻开看看，他会作何反应？"

# game/day 7.rpy:470
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_61453109:

    # ju "「...Oh, this.{p} I think it's something I should bring,\n if we're going to the beach.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 62-64)
    ju "「……这个啊……这些是我觉得，\n我们去海边应该带的东西。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:471
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_0d7e3b86:

    # fn "「Isn't that a lot?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 66-67)
    fn "「这个不会太多了吧？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:475
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_0bfa1940:

    # ju "「Isn't this how much you'd usually bring?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 70-71)
    ju "「你平时不是也会带这么多么？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:476
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_62fdc575:

    # "If he says so, then it must be."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 73)
    "既然他这么说，那就一定是了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:477
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_9724d986:

    # fn "「But I don't have any goggles...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 75-76)
    fn "「但是我没有潜水镜……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:481
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_56f8b01b:

    # ju "「If I have to...{p} I'll let you borrow a spare.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 81-82)
    ju "「如果必要的话……{p}我可以借给你一副。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:485
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_d865cfd5:

    # "From a parasol to a straw mat, he has everything.{p}He even has enough goggles for everybody...{p}Is there a reason why?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 85-87)
    "从阳伞到凉席，他几乎什么都带了。{p}他甚至给每个人都带了一副潜水镜……{p}我真想知道为什么。"

# game/day 7.rpy:486
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_ef00525e:

    # "But will I be able to use Juuichi-san's spare?{p}I hope they're normal ones,\nbut they'll slip off if they're made for beastmen."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 89-90)
    "但是我能用柔一君的那副眼镜么？{p}如果是按照熊人设计的，那一定会很容易地滑掉的。"

# game/day 7.rpy:491
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_d78f0b19:

    # ka "「Looks like you guys got here early.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 95-96)
    ka "「看来你们来的很早嘛。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:492
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_c850cd00:

    # fn "「Oh, Kouya.{p} Good morning.{p} You're early, too.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 98-100)
    fn "「噢，{w=.3}洸哉。{p}早上好。{p}你来得不也很早么。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:496
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_d50cdbce:

    # ka "「I wouldn't have been on time,\n if I didn't get here early.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 104-105)
    ka "「如果我不早来的话，我肯定会迟到的。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:497
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_833824ae:

    # who "「Good morning.{p} It's unusual for you to be early.{p} I hope it doesn't rain.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 108-110)
    who "「早上好。{p}你能这么早来真不寻常啊。{p}希望今天不会下雨。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:501
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_8ac8495a:

    # fn "「Good morning, Shin-kun.{p} I like to get up early for trips.{p} That's why.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 114-117)
    fn "「深，早上好。{p}我喜欢在出游前早起，\n就这样。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:505
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_c57c9346:

    # si "「You still have some growing up to do.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 122)
    si "「你还有一些成长的烦恼需要处理呢。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:506
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_bcf8ec61:

    # fn "「That's...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 124-125)
    fn "「这个……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:510
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_6864c5e0:

    # si "「I'm just joking.{p} It's natural that you'd get here early.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 128-130)
    si "「开玩笑啦。{p}你能起这么早还是很正常的。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:514
