# game/day 7.rpy:544
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_eb9f7297:

    # ky "「Good morning.{p} I could hear Tatsuki-san's voice\n from all the way over there.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 173-176)
    ky "「早上好。{p}我老远就听到辰树的声音了。\n如我所料，你们这么早就到了啊。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:545
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_e26727ff:

    # ky "「So I already knew that you guys\n were gathering before I arrived.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 175-176)
    ky "「如我所料，你们这么早就到了啊。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:549
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_a3a5deef:

    # so "「Everybody is so early!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 179-180)
