# game/day 7.rpy:560
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_eb978638:

    # su "「Yeah, he came over and got me.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 199-200)
    su "「是啊，他来接的我。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:561
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_ba342c32:

    # ky "「It's the same direction from Tarou's house,{p} so he came along with us today.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 202-204)
