# game/day 7.rpy:609
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_5d84ae29:

    # to "「It's nothing. I just went to get him,\n and he was still eating,\n then long, long after that...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 264-266)
    to "「没什么，我就是去找他，\n那时他还在吃饭，\n然后很久很久之后……」"

