translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_9acefcf3:

    # ko "「Hahaha, sorry. There just happened to be\n something good on TV.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 269-271)
    ko "「哈哈哈，对不起，正好电视里有好看的节目。\n然后就是我走之前，我想检查下我带的东西。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:614
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_ca356109:

    # ko "「Also, I wanted to check over\n what I'm bringing before I left.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 269-271)
    ko "「还有就是，在我走之前，\n我想检查下我带的东西。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:618
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_c86d913e:

    # to "「...Didn't I tell you\n when I was going to come get you?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 274-275)
