    # si "「I think you should have gotten here\n earlier than the planned meeting time.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 286-287)
    si "「换句话说，我觉得你们应该会来得比计划得还要早。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:634
