# game/day 7.rpy:671
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_b0cbb1be:

    # ko "「I discovered it by chance the other day,\n so I checked it out.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 347-349)
    ko "「那条路是我有一次不经意发现的，\n所以我就去检查了下。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:672
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_ce1ba437:

    # su "「That's a great discovery, isn't it?{p} It's wonderful!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 353-355)
    su "「这不是一个重大的发现么？{p}那真是棒极了！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:673
translate chinese_simplified beach07_meetup_3a314013:

    # ky "「I'm pretty sure there's a river around here.\n It must be the source of the big river\n that flows through Minasato.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 359-361)
    ky "「我很确定在这附近有条河，\n它一定是横穿水乡，那条大河的源头。」"

