# game/day 7.rpy:1031
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_204183fa:

    # ka "If we take it too easy,{p} we won't have done anything,{p} and it'll be over.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1449)
    ka "如果我们不拊紧的话，{p}那么到时候啥都干不了了。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1035
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_a458c9a8:

    # "Kouya laughed as he walked out.{p}I followed after."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1453-1454)
    "洸哉笑着走了出去。{p}我紧随其后。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1036
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_4debdb2d:

    # "The two of us got in line\nfor the changing rooms."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1454)
    "一同向更衣室走去。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1040
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_49cffd8b:

    # "The changing rooms weren't that impressive.{p}They looked like they could be blown away."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1457-1458)
    "这间更衣室给人的印象并不深刻，{p}毕竟它破得好像一阵风就能带走的样子。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1041
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_4021f6a2:

    # "I got in and took my swimsuit out of my luggage.{p}I thought 'time to get changed',{p}but then my hand stopped."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1460-1462)
    "等我进去时，我从行李里拿出了我的泳衣，{p}终于可以换衣服了，本来是这样想的，{p}但是却不知不觉的停了下来。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1042
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_b85147fc:

    # "As for why I stopped,{p}there wasn't much reason."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1464)
    "至于我为什么停了下来，这个大家都懂的。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1046
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_6fdd2752:

    # ka "「What's wrong, [fn]?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1468-1469)
    ka "「怎么了，[fn]？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1047
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_eaf430ac:

    # fn "「Oh uh, nothing?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1471-1472)
    fn "「哦，呃，没什么？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1048
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_81defc4d:

    # ka "「Really?{p} Well okay.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1474-1475)
    ka "「是么？{p}没事就好。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1052
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_87587ad6:

    # "That was why I stopped.{p}It was nothing but him changing clothes."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1479-1480)
    "我就是为了这个才停下来的，{p}他在换衣服。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1053
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_de7460dc:

    # "Like I thought,{p}a person changing quickly\nisn't much of a sight."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1481)
    "我觉得，如果迅速地换好衣服，会错过不少风景呢。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1054
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_1bffebad:

    # "Is it a loss to look and have to leave it?{p}That's what I think, but then I also think...{p}That it isn't right."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1483-1484)
    "话说虽然只是看着，但是是不是有些太不好呢？{p}确实。突然觉得……这是不对的。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1055
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_59c01a22:

    # "My mind is conflicted...{p}Hm, but is it okay to look...{p}Just a little...?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1485-1487)
    "我的内心正在进行激烈的斗争……{p}呃，不过……{w=.3}少看一点还是没关系的吧……？"

# game/day 7.rpy:1056
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_7799a4f0:

    # fn "「Yeah, it's all right...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1489-1490)
    fn "「嗯，没关系……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1057
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_c72830b9:

    # "I muttered so no one could hear, and decided."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1492)
    "我窃窃私语，就这么定了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1058
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_8d7e0800:

    # "Mom, Dad, I am a bad child!{p}I've become filthy!{p}But I have no regrets!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1494-1496)
    "爸，妈，[fn]让你们失望了！{p}我现在好篓琕啊！{p}但是我一点都不后悔！"

# game/day 7.rpy:1059
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_fb188f9d:

    # "As I continued changing,{p}I looked at Kouya from the side,{p}as though I didn't notice."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1498-1499)
    "当我还在换衣服的时候，{p}瞟了一下洸哉那边。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1063
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_c14a9da7:

    # "Wait, he's already done!?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1503)
    "他早就换好了？！"

# game/day 7.rpy:1064
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_e498672a:

    # "Eh, what is this?{p}What trick did he pull?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1505-1506)
    "呃，{w=.3}什么时候，{w=.3}什么时候完成的？{p}他究竟是在什么时候完成的？"

# game/day 7.rpy:1065
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_be00d5a1:

    # "When did Kouya get so good\nat time management?{p}I-is he a new Stand User!?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1507)
    "这可不是抢车位啊喂！？"

# game/day 7.rpy:1069
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_21fcf2e3:

    # ka "「Hmm? You still haven't changed, [fn]?{p} You'll get left behind.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1510-1512)
    ka "「哇？{p}你还没换好啊，[fn]。{p}那我先走咯。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1070
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_b38a44fa:

    # fn "「Whuh!?{p} He-hey wait!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1514-1515)
    fn "「喂？！{p}等、{w=.3}等一下！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1074
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_23c0768d:

    # "Kouya left me behind,{p}promptly picked up his clothes,{p}and put them behind the changing rooms."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1519-1520)
    "洸哉立即拿起了衣服，{p}扔到了更衣室后面，走了出去。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1075
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_3c385ca3:

    # "Almost exactly done in the blink of an eye."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1521)
    "这几乎是一眨眼的功夫完成的。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1076
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_2ab6ae32:

    # fn "「...From here on,{p} I won't waver and just stare.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1523-1524)
    fn "「……从这时起，{p}我不再踔躇，要直勾勾地盯着他的背影。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1077
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_853befd2:

    # "Being left alone,{p}I decided that with all my heart."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1526)
    "他走之后，我下定了决心。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1083
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_59fce36f:

    # "I lagged behind Kouya a little,{p}and came outside too.{p}But I don't see him anywhere."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1537-1538)
    "紧随其后，也出来了。{p}但是我到处都找不到他。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1084
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_d17df2dd:

    # fn "「Huh, was I really left behind?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1540-1541)
    fn "「呃，我是真的被丢下了么？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1085
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_5e021203:

    # "I got anxious, and looked around the area."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1543)
    "我紧张地环顾四周。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1086
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_c69d37d1:

    # "There's people playing beach volleyball,{p}people playing in the shallow water..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1545-1546)
    "有人在打排球，{p}有人在水洼里嬉戏……"

# game/day 7.rpy:1087
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_80f8887c:

    # "And unlike the others,{p}there are people swimming\nin the opposite side."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1548-1549)
    "但是还有与众不同的，{p}比如那个仰面朝上，漂在海面上的家伙。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1088
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_42d2b863:

    # "It seems everyone's enjoying\nthemselves as they please here."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1551)
    "因为能来海边玩，大家都玩得很开心。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1089
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_3cb9b691:

    # "Importantly, Kouya is..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1553)
    "重要的是，洸哉他……"

# game/day 7.rpy:1090
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_7fc12734:

    # fn "「...Ah, I see him.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1555-1556)
    fn "「……啊、{w=.3}找到了。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1091
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_44ef43a0:

    # "Kouya was floating face up on top of the sea."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1558)
    "洸哉就是那个仰面浮在海面上的家伙。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1092
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_89f8c635:

    # "He was cradled by the waves,{p}as if he was naturally part of the ocean.{p}Somehow, he seemed to be in a good mood."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1559-1560)
    "他随着海浪一起摇曳着，就如同是大海的一部分。{p}看起来他的心情不错呢。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1093
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_a8488a6f:

    # "As I watched,{p}inside me a mischievous idea was born."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1562)
    "这时，心中萌生了一个想法。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1094
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_cf2e6d14:

    # "As revenge for being ditched,{p}I'll surprise him a bit."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1563)
    "作为对他撇下我的报复，我准备去吓他一下。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1095
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_58e95030:

    # "From the point I was left behind,{p}I moved and entered the sea."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1565-1566)
    "于是我便慢慢地走到了海里。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1096
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_97b48239:

    # "Then, so I wouldn't be noticed,{p}I got down low and approached Kouya.{p}Slowly, slowly."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1568-1570)
    "我游到洸哉的下面，这样一定不会被发现的。{p}渐渐的，渐渐的，{p}离洸哉越来越近了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1097
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_0ea69c6e:

    # "The distance to Kouya gradually shortened,{p}and if I claw at the water's surface,{p}the splash should reach him."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1572-1573)
    "如果我抓一下水面，{p}水花一定会溅到他。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1098
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_667fe720:

    # "However, Kouya's looking at the sky,{p}just as usual."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1575)
    "但是洸哉仍然一如既往地望着天。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1099
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_9966ac2f:

    # "He won't notice me here.{p}This is so convenient."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1576-1577)
    "他肯定不会发现我在这里的。{p}这太方便了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1100
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_a0e31791:

    # "Silently, but with all my strength,{p}I sucked my breath in."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1579)
    "默默的，我用尽全身力气，屏住呼吸。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1101
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_0b502ee9:

    # "And just as silently,{p}my body went under into the water."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1580)
    "然后悄悄地把身子沉到了水下。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1102
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_9515516c:

    # "Since it's not that deep yet,{p}my feet touched the ground."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1582)
    "一直沉到我的双脚碰到了海床。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1103
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_d6d2d507:

    # "I kicked the cold sand,{p}and swam across the floor over Kouya."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1583-1584)
    "我用力蹬了一下那冰冷的沙子，{p}窜过了洸哉下面。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1104
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_b54e69b5:

    # "When I look up, I see his tufty tail,{p}being cradled in the waves."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1586)
    "在我向上看时，我见到了他那柔软的尾巴在水中摇曳。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1105
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_7e6db66f:

    # "Just like I thought it would.{p}Without meaning to, my cheeks slackened."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1587-1589)
    "这正如我所愿。{p}不知不觉的，我的臀部放松了下来。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1106
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_834b4f66:

    # "Now then, it's about time I pull my prank."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1590)
    "现在，好戏就要上演了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1107
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_1f4ac737:

    # "The old people have said it.{p}If a string is hanging from the ceiling,{p}just pull on it and see what happens."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1592-1593)
    "俗话说得好，{p}吊在天花板上的绳子，不妨一拉。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1108
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_4fca31d5:

    # "In this case...{nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1595)
    "这样的话……"

# game/day 7.rpy:1112
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_c33afbff:

    # fn "{size=+20}「HIYAAAHH!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1598-1599)
    fn "「哄呀——！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1113
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_8592ef0d:

    # "One shout,{p}turned into nothing but a bubbling murmur."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1601-1602)
    "这一声大喊，并没有什么效果，{p}成了水泡中的呢喃。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1118
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_1d17205a:

    # "I reached out for the base of Kouya's tail.{w} {nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1603)
    "我伸出手抓住了洸哉的尾巴。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1120
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_3d1a9ff7:

    # extend "{w=.01}{nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1605-1607)
    extend "我一把抓住，然后快速地捏了捏。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1123
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_7815f0dd:

    # ka "{size=+15}「Whuh!?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1610-1611)
    ka "「哈啊啊——！？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1124
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_3639ed16:

    # "Kouya jumped in surprise."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1613-1614)
    "洸哉真是被吓了一跳。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1125
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_601e5800:

    # "His feet floundered,{p}as if he was searching for solid ground."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1615)
    "他的脚步凌乱了，好像在寻找任何一个可以站住的地方。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1126
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_b2faedd8:

    # "To get him so freaked out\nsomehow feels refreshing.{p}Yeah, I got him good."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1617-1619)
    "这可把他吓坏了，这让我感觉甚爽。{p}嘿嘿，我做到了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1127
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_aecd5203:

    # "Soon after Kouya's feet hit the sand,{p}he stood up."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1621)
    "很快洸哉的脚碰到了沙地，站稳了身子。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1128
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_7a36bfad:

    # "After checking to make sure,{p}I surfaced."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1622)
    "我觉得安全了些，便就现身了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1134
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_9dfa65ec:

    # ka "「Who'd have thought it...{p} [fn].」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1626-1627)
    ka "「谁干的，我觉得……{p}是你吧，{w=.3}[fn]」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1135
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_ef4cb1fd:

    # "Kouya said that faintly,{p}while he was catching his breath."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1629-1630)
    "洸哉一边调整着那惊恐的呼吸，{p}一边虚弱地说。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1136
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_bc15c833:

    # fn "「Correct, it was me.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1632-1633)
    fn "「没错，就是我」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1137
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_18776741:

    # ka "「Still with the stupid stuff...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1635-1636)
    ka "「又是……这倒霉的尾巴……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1138
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_d66e62c2:

    # fn "「But that's because you really ditched me.{p} I got a revelation from God, saying that\n paying you back one time would be all right.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1638-1641)
    fn "「那是因为你丢下我先跑了，{p}然后我收到了天神的启示，{p}让我这样做来惩罚你。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1142
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_440eaa39:

    # ka "「Wrong, it was from an evil god.{p} Don't listen to the voices.{p} Don't do what they say.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1644-1645)
    ka "「给你指示的一定是个恶魔。{p}不能他说什么，{p}你就做什么。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1143
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_ab4885d2:

    # fn "「I'll only put in effort next time.{p} Anyway, that was a good reaction back there.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1647-1649)
    fn "「我下次还会听他的哦。{p}而且还会经常干哦，还有你的反应还不错哦。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1144
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_e92d1399:

    # fn "「Now I know your tail is weak.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1650)
    fn "「我知道了，你的尾巴就是弱点。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1148
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_1ba670e8:

    # ka "「Nope.{p} It's because you suddenly grabbed it.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1653-1655)
    ka "「才不是。{p}那是因为你突然去抓它罢了。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1149
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_f0b868b6:

    # "Well, I guess that's true too.{p}The tail seems to be connected to their spine,\nso they would be sensitive to it."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1657-1659)
    "不过我也觉得有些道理。{p}尾巴貌似是直接连着脊椎的，所以它才会这么敏感。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1150
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_e24ebce2:

    # "However, after finishing this prank,\nsomehow it feels unfinished.{p}So for a little longer, I bothered Kouya."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1661-1663)
    "然后，只是这样捅弄他的话，似乃还不够有趣。{p}我还可以更进一步地捅弄一下他。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1151
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_c2caf249:

    # "I've already had to chase after Kouya,{p}so I was ready to run."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1665-1666)
    "反正一定会被他追，{p}先做好随时开溞的准备。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1152
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_f70f7e25:

    # "While I was thinking about that,\nI threw one last line at Kouya."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1669-1670)
    "我一边在脑中打着坏主意，一边对洸哉吐出必杀的话。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1153
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_85564632:

    # fn "「Hmph.{p} Well, you made a great face.{p} Maybe I'll tell Torahiko how to do it too.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1672-1675)
    fn "「呜——{p}洸哉你刚才的表情很精彩嘛，{p}或许我会跟虎彦分享分享哦。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1157
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_e530c02e:

    # ka "「...Wait just a minute, [fn].」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1678-1679)
    ka "「……等一下，[fn]」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1158
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_73a4b51a:

    # "Yes..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1681)
    "——哟——咿——"

# game/day 7.rpy:1159
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_e32521c3:

    # fn "「Eh?{p} Oh hey, perfect timing.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1683-1685)
    fn "「诶——？{p}啊，{w=.3}说曹操曹操到。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1160
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_d83d4638:

    # fn "「Torahiko's right over there.{p} Hey! Torahiko!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1686)
    fn "喂——虎彦——！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1164
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_430c0b47:

    # "I began running with all my power."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1690-1691)
    "话音刚落，{p}我就撒丫子向那边跑去。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1168
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_888d317e:

    # "\nBoom."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1694)
    "——咒。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1169
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_c25513de:

    # ka "{size=+15}「You wait right there, [fn]!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1696-1697)
    ka "「喂，等、等一下，[fn]！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1170
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_95d54dce:

    # fn "「No way!{p} I'm not going to wait at all!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1699-1700)
    fn "「没门！{p}才不会停下来呢！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1171
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_983167a1:

    # "And then, this oceanside game of tag began,\njust as planned."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1702-1703)
    "现在，海边的追逐拉开了战幕，正如我所愿。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1172
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kouya_f3e2ebf5:

    # "I'm always getting teased by Kouya.\nDoing this once in while is fine, right?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1705-1706)
    "我总是被洸哉戏弄，现在反过来戏弄他，挺有趣不是么？"

# game/day 7.rpy:1186
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_04c5dea0:

    # "Anyway the beach is here,{p}but if they notice everyone will go on ahead."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1031-1032)
    "总算是到了海边，{p}但是如果他们都先到了，"

# game/day 7.rpy:1187
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_dabc2e45:

    # "If I get left behind in that case,{p}I'll chase after them."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1033-1034)
    "而我却不小心的落在了后面，{p}我肯定会追上他们的。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1188
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_8f16e2c5:

    # "Which reminds me, Shun-kun's clothes,{p}are blue and white,{p}the color of the sky and sea!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1036)
    "峻蓝白相间的衣服，让我想起，这就是天空和大海的颜色啊！"

# game/day 7.rpy:1189
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_e38c062f:

    # "I wonder what his swimsuit's like!{p}Those thoughts started up,{p}and the search for him on the beach began."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1037-1038)
    "我真想知道他的泳衣是什么颜色的！！{p}一旦萌生了这种念头，就开始在沙滩上寻找峻的踪迹。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1190
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_a20cefa7:

    # "..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1039)
    "……"

# game/day 7.rpy:1191
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_3a306a33:

    # "Ah, there he is."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1040)
    "呵，他在那里啊。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1192
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_223d78a3:

    # "On top of a leisure seat on the beach,{p}sitting while holding his knee,{p}enjoying the salty air."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1040-1041)
    "坐在一个沙滩席上，{p}抱着膝盖，正享受着带有淡淡咸味的海风。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1193
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_975d9db2:

    # "That soft whipping sound I hear,{p}it's coming from his tail,{p}hitting the ground."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1043-1044)
    "我能听到温柔的敲打声，{p}那是他的尾巴，在敲打着地面。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1194
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_22d95ef6:

    # su "「Ocean, ocean!{p} Swimming, floating, diving,{p} scubasailing!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1054-1056)
    su "「大海啊{p}大海啊！{p}游泳啊{p}浪花啊{p}玩水啊{p}汪呜！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1195
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_a20cefa7_1:

    # "..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1058)
    "……"

# game/day 7.rpy:1196
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_22d95ef6_1:

    # su "「Ocean, ocean!{p} Swimming, floating, diving,{p} scubasailing!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1061-1063)
    su "「大海啊{p}大海啊！{p}游泳啊{p}浪花啊{p}玩水啊{p}汪呜！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1197
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_3dcc3c4f:

    # "...What's scubasailing?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1065)
    "……这个汪呜是什么？"

# game/day 7.rpy:1201
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_e6f21e07:

    # su "「[fn]-san!{p} I'm done readying up!{p} Let's go swimming!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1069-1070)
    su "「[fn]！{p}我已经准备好了！{p}一起游泳吧！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1202
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_615c5d73:

    # "Shun-kun grabbed my surprised self,{p}and shouted out in a clear voice.{p}...What did he get ready?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1072-1074)
    "峻拉着惊讶的我，{p}兴奋地叫道。{p}……他什么准备好了？"

# game/day 7.rpy:1209
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_75ebd5e4:

    # "He pulled my arm to a changing room,{p}and we entered a little shack."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1084-1085)
    "他牵着我的胳膊进了更衣室，{p}也就是一个简陋的小棚子。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1213
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_d8b92be7:

    # su "「Ocean, ocean...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1089)
    su "「大海啊{p}大海啊」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1214
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_41b597b9:

    # "Shun-kun's song is in its 6th repeat,{p}but it's okay."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1091-1092)
    "峻的这首歌已经重复第6遍了。{p}不过还好了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1215
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_0d6bced3:

    # "Today's main show is the live changing,{p}of a childhood friend (of 5 years.)"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1093)
    "今天的重头戏就是儿时的朋友的现场更衣表演。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1216
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_d4932832:

    # "As the rest of the group have already left,{p}and jumped into the water,{p}let us carefully observe."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1095-1097)
    "当其他人已经离开，{p}并且跳到海里去玩的时候，{p}就剩我可以好好观察了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1220
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_29d6e8f3:

    # su "「Scubasailing!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1101)
    su "「うきゅるーん♪」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1221
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_3ca6bcd0:

    # "The beginning starts with a wrap towel.{nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1103)
    "他拿出了一卷毛巾，就叫做毛巾卷好了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1225
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_aefbd375:

    # su "「[fn]-san,{p} you aren't going to change?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1109)
    su "「[fn]？{p}你还不换衣服么？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1226
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_74bfdb43:

    # fn "「Y-yeah.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1112)
    fn "「换、{w=.3}换换」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1227
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_96032737:

    # "...So, shall I start taking my clothes off too?{p}I have to make sure not to miss my best shot."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1114-1115)
    "那么……我是不是也该脱衣服了？{p}还得确保会有最好的观察角度。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1231
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_ab54fec1:

    # su "「Nyan nyan nyan nyan nyan!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1119)
    su "「啰啰啰——啰啰啰啰——」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1232
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_ee0f063c:

    # "Seems to be an interlude."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1121)
    "唱到间奏了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1233
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_47050d5f:

    # "Shun-kun took off his outer clothes,{p}patted and folded them,{p}then placed them on the tatami mat."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1122-1123)
    "峻脱掉了他的外套，{p}叭哒叭哒地叠成皱皱的样子，放在那里。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1234
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_81c44309:

    # "What a delicate body.{p}You could almost feel,{p}the slenderness of his shoulder."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1125-1126)
    "好娇嫩的身体啊。{p}那细小的肩膀把我吸引了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1235
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_06fb5e5f:

    # "Yeah, stick your arm into the towel,{p}and while you're at that,{p}take your underwear off."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1128-1129)
    "对对，就是那样，把手腕从毛巾中间插进去，{p}再扭扭捏捏地把短裤脱下来。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1236
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_f695acbf:

    # "As I thought,{p}he's wearing white briefs.{p}Mhmm."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1130)
    "果然还穿着白色的短内裤呢，嗯嗯。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1241
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_b8ef403e:

    # "And then when his legs go through the swimsuit,{p}his wrap towel slips a little.{p}...You can see his crotch from here!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1136-1137)
    "当他把腿穿入泳裤时候，卷毛巾稍微露出了一点儿，{p}……在这里可以看到他的裆部！"

# game/day 7.rpy:1242
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_fc51bc42:

    # su "「U-urg... Hrm...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1142)
    su "「呜，{w=.3}呜哇……嗯啾……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1243
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_f72a3042:

    # "Shun-kun has become a little confused,{p}and embarrassed as he pulls up his towel.{p}Now he's pulling it up each leg at a time."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1144-1146)
    "峻开始有些手足无措了，慌张并害羞地拉起毛巾。{p}一只脚一只脚地将膝盖提起来，{p}将泳裤好好穿好之后，再将卷毛巾脱下来吧。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1244
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_2ab3bd4d:

    # "Since his swim trunks are not firmly in place,{p}let's take off the towel."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1146)
    "将泳裤好好穿好之后，再将卷毛巾脱下来吧。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1245
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_510484da:

    # su "「*Mumble*.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1149)
    su "「呒咕呒咕……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1246
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_6117ed3a:

    # "Now that the towel has been lifted,{p}up over the head and taken off..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1151)
    "当他把卷毛巾向上拉，想要从头上脱下来的时候，"

# game/day 7.rpy:1247
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_b994e6d7:

    # fn "「Shun-kun, that looks so good on you.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1156)
    fn "「峻君，{w=.3}很适合你哦。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1248
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_ce3f4578:

    # su "「Really?{p} But this is what I always wear.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1159)
    su "「真的么？{p}我一直就是这样穿着呢。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1249
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_295d3c28:

    # "After politely putting away the towel,{p}he's now putting on a yellow swim cap."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1161)
    "他小心地取下毛巾后，现在正在戴一个黄色的泳帽。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1250
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_e243b455:

    # "Bring that old swimsuit out here,{p}to your Onii-san,{p}so I can reuse it for the sake of Earth."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1169-1171)
    "为了保护地球的生态环境，{p}将这件旧泳衣拿到哥哥我这里来吧。{p}经年累月的起毛和延伸而出的橡胶，一定是一顿美餐呢。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1254
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_bedd8d3d:

    # "Shun-kun appeared wearing the stock school swimsuit."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1179)
    "穿着学校统一定制的泳衣的峻君出现了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1255
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_2b6d1aae:

    # "Yes, I've already set my expectations,{p}but this is also splendid."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1183)
    "嗯，虽然已经预想过多次了，不过仍然是相当养眼。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1259
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_b785bdba:

    # su "「The white ones were too tight,\n so I didn't want to wear them.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1187-1188)
    su "「[fn]，{p}那件白的，有点太紧了，所以……我不准备穿那件。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1260
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_492f5337:

    # su "「That's not weird, is it...?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1189)
    su "「这件的话，会不会很奇怪？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1265
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_4e978474:

    # "{size=+30}!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1196)
    "！"

# game/day 7.rpy:1269
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_153482a5:

    # "That's what I call a swimmer guy!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1201-1202)
    "这难道就是俗话所说的……{p}游泳辅助裤！"

# game/day 7.rpy:1270
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_d9466007:

    # "Once again, I stare at that bulge."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1207)
    "我重新打量着那膨胀的部分，"

# game/day 7.rpy:1271
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_e9c95352:

    # "He's still not aware of it,\npushing itself along the outline\nof the slippery cloth."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1208-1209)
    "尚在发育之中的竹筒，被滑滑的衣料压着，谦虚地主张着它的轮廓。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1272
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_73c01275:

    # "Ergh, this is dangerous after all.{p}In a typical summer at a beach like this..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1218-1220)
    "唔唔唔，实在是太危险了。{p}放任将这深蓝色的黑匣子少年的肉块到开放的夏日沙滩之中的话，实在是让人感觉不甚安全。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1273
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_44494f49:

    # "It can really influence one\ninto releasing that juvenile body.{p}There's no mistake."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1222-1224,1230)
    "十有八九会被有某种兴趣的奇怪人士带到大石头的阴影之中，被这样隔着布料地舔弄一番之后，在下海之前，只有那一个部件被染上深深的水色。{p}不会有错的。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1274
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_89a11742:

    # "My eyes are too rooted to the spot,{p}it wouldn't be good if he became aware\nof my... Uhh... Observational skills."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1237-1239)
    "不、不过，那可爱的、颤动的，既会柔软又会硬硬的部位，就这样在阳光的照射下晃来晃去，……也是美景一件。{p}视线完全被吸引，潜在的正太控之魂也可以瞬间觉醒，海滩必将大乱。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1275
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shun_c33035ea:

    # "What do I do?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1241)
    "我该怎么办？"

# game/day 7.rpy:1285
translate chinese_simplified beach07_buckleup_643e117c:

    # "I'll do it for the sake of dignity."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1274-1276)
    "只是因为青色的膨胀就方寸大乱。{p}控制不住自己灼灼地进行着如此这般的视奸，不能这样啊！！{p}这简直是对神圣的鼠蹊部的亵渎！"

# game/day 7.rpy:1286
translate chinese_simplified beach07_buckleup_6a7bdd59:

    # fn "「Maybe, it's better to put on the white ones,{p} since they won't let anything important get broken.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1278-1280)
    fn "「或许，你穿这件白的会更好些，毕竟它不会引起一些什么奇怪的那啥。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1287
translate chinese_simplified beach07_buckleup_f3ee9833:

    # su "「B-but...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1282-1283)
    su "「但、{w=.3}但是——」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1288
translate chinese_simplified beach07_buckleup_689e0bdd:

    # fn "「Tatsu-nii's wearing those too.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1285-1286)
    fn "「辰兄也是穿这个啊。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1289
translate chinese_simplified beach07_buckleup_5aeaf8d6:

    # "On the opposite side is Tatsu-nii,{p}who looks like he hasn't changed yet."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1288)
    "辰兄就在背后，看起来他还没有换衣服。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1290
translate chinese_simplified beach07_buckleup_603ccb3d:

    # "He's taking off his clothes,{p}getting out and putting on a white fundoshi,{p}and he diligently checks the knot."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1289-1290)
    "他正在脱衣服，然后换上了一条六尺裤，接着就在细心地检查绳结。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1291
translate chinese_simplified beach07_buckleup_10db39e0:

    # "It doesn't look any different,{p}from the underwear he took off though.{p}...Maybe it's water resistant?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1292-1293)
    "自从他脱掉内衣以来，看着没什么变化。{p}……或者说这是防水的？"

# game/day 7.rpy:1295
translate chinese_simplified beach07_buckleup_29fb9e2b:

    # su "「Uguu.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1297-1298)
    su "「嗯。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1296
translate chinese_simplified beach07_buckleup_4a9f11cf:

    # fn "「C'mon, I think the white ones,{p} are important after all.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1300-1301)
    fn "「看吧，我就觉得白的这件更好啦。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1300
translate chinese_simplified beach07_buckleup_3b405425:

    # su "「I-I understand.{p} If [fn]-san says so...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1305-1307)
    su "「我，我知道了。既然[fn]这么说……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1301
translate chinese_simplified beach07_buckleup_1d885771:

    # "Shun-kun's obedient.{p}He's rummaging for the wrap towel from before.{p}Now, time to watch live changing again!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1309-1311)
    "峻很顺从的服从了我。{p}他开始到处寻找他那条卷起来的毛巾。{p}那么，现在就是现场脱衣秀咯！"

# game/day 7.rpy:1305
translate chinese_simplified beach07_buckleup_876b6ab7:

    # ta "「Hey let's go [fn]!{p} Summer is calling to me!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1314-1315)
    ta "「嘿，走吧，[fn]！{p}夏天在召唤我们！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1306
translate chinese_simplified beach07_buckleup_0655ff44:

    # fn "「Wait, I'm not done changing yet.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1317-1318)
    fn "「等等，我还没换好衣服。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1307
translate chinese_simplified beach07_buckleup_e4f72762:

    # "Srtch srtch srtch.{p}The sounds of my body dragging along."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1320)
    "我奋力地脱着衣服，"

# game/day 7.rpy:1308
translate chinese_simplified beach07_buckleup_1df63f90:

    # "Up until my clothes got dumped into the water,{p}Tatsu-nii wouldn't let go of the back of my neck."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1321-1322)
    "而辰兄一直站在我的背后，直到我收拾好脱下来的衣服后，才让我走。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1317
translate chinese_simplified beach07_hangloose_c1e15895:

    # "Okay.{p}I have to tell everyone how great this is."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1334-1335)
    "好极了！{p}好东西应该大家齐分享才是嘛。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1318
translate chinese_simplified beach07_hangloose_95380ef3:

    # fn "「Yep!{p} If it's not uncomfortable, it's okay!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1337-1339)
    fn "「嗯！{p}这看着一点儿都不难受，挺舒服的不是吗！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1322
translate chinese_simplified beach07_hangloose_1d9c9409:

    # su "「Ahaha, I'll go on ahead then.{p} [fn]-san, please hurry on over too!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1343-1345)
    su "「啊哈哈，我先走了哈！{p}[fn]也要快一点儿哦！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1326
translate chinese_simplified beach07_hangloose_ab45afdf:

    # "Shun-kun said that and rushed out energetically."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1355)
    "峻说着就兴冲冲地跑了出去。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1327
translate chinese_simplified beach07_hangloose_ec7dd09f:

    # "After taking off the clothes he usually wears,{p}the sight of light brown,{p}with blue and yellow accents is dazzling."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1356-1357)
    "脱掉了平时穿的衣服后的他，棕色的眼瞳里，闪耀着蓝的和黄色的音符。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1328
translate chinese_simplified beach07_hangloose_50bea24a:

    # "His wagging tail and figure,{p}matched in with the sky and sea.{p}It made for some awesome scenery."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1359-1361)
    "他的身躯和摇晃的尾巴，融入了碧海蓝天，形成了一幅绝妙的景象。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1332
translate chinese_simplified beach07_hangloose_48f0f392:

    # ju "「Hey, Kodori.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1365-1366)
    ju "「喂——古酉」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1336
translate chinese_simplified beach07_hangloose_a9fe3faa:

    # su "「Yes, Juuichi-san?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1370-1371)
    su "「什么事情，柔一君？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1337
translate chinese_simplified beach07_hangloose_66ed2c1e:

    # "Is the sightseeing-pamphlet worthy scene,{p}Juuichi-san, in his casual swimsuit,{p}called and stopped Shun-kun."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1373-1374)
    "这样美妙的景象真应该出一个绘本，穿着泳衣的柔一叫住了峻，"

# game/day 7.rpy:1338
translate chinese_simplified beach07_hangloose_9d1b773e:

    # "He's whispering something into his ears."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1375)
    "在他的耳边低语着什么。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1342
translate chinese_simplified beach07_hangloose_05c2754f:

    # "Shun-kun looked a little surprised,{p}and he returned to the changing room,{p}as his shoulders dropped."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1383-1384)
    "峻看起来有些惊讶，然后回到了更衣室，肩膀也耷拉了下来。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1346
translate chinese_simplified beach07_hangloose_3e03c184:

    # su "「Fine... I'll put on a supporter...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1387-1388)
    su "「还好啦……我会撑一下的……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1347
translate chinese_simplified beach07_hangloose_4adb66ce:

    # "He pulled out his wrap towel,{p}and put it on his lower back again.{p}Then, Juuichi-san sluggishly showed up."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1390-1391)
    "他拉出了那卷毛巾，塞到了它掉下来的地方。{p}然后，柔一缓缓地走了进来。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1351
translate chinese_simplified beach07_hangloose_1e8197e6:

    # ju "「[ln], didn't you notice?{p} Kodori, you didn't put on a supporter did you?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1394-1396)
    ju "「[西村]，你就没有发现么？{p}古酉，你是不是少了个毛巾把它撑起来？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1352
translate chinese_simplified beach07_hangloose_e397a52a:

    # fn "「Oh!{p} I see it, now!{p} I completely, entirely didn't notice!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1398-1400)
    fn "「喔！{p}我现在才发现！{p}我真的刚才没注意到！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1356
translate chinese_simplified beach07_hangloose_9f18d18f:

    # ju "「[ln]!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1403-1404)
    ju "「[西村]」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1357
translate chinese_simplified beach07_hangloose_bab2a10a:

    # fn "「I'm so sorry.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1406-1407)
    fn "「抱歉。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1358
translate chinese_simplified beach07_hangloose_6e6a550b:

    # "He saw through my fickle motives,{p}and I hung my head in defeat,{p}from his silent heavy pressure."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1409-1410)
    "他识破了我的动机，{p}在他肃杀的沉默中，我低下头亮起了白旗。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1373
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shin_b98e4eb9:

    # "Anyway, everyone's changed into swimsuits,{p}and came back to the beach."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3144)
    "不管怎样，大家都换掉了泳衣，回到了岸上。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1374
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shin_b844352f:

    # "If there's a chance,{p}I'd take advantage of the changing,{p}to sneak a peek at everyone."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3146)
    "如果有机会的话，我要偷窥每个人，嘿嘿。{p}"

# game/day 7.rpy:1375
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shin_b335efe7:

    # "How would that go anyway?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3147)
    "不过怎样才能有机会呢？"

# game/day 7.rpy:1376
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shin_ae2e174b:

    # "While I was lost thinking about that,{p}everyone had already finished changing,{p}leaving me for last."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3148)
    "等我反应过来时，大家早已经换完了衣服，只剩下我一个了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1377
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shin_7d0f7fa6:

    # "Dammit! When we go back,{p}I'll definitely look.{p}I'll look for sure!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3150-3151)
    "讨厌！等大家回去时，我一定要看到。{p}一定会看到的！"

# game/day 7.rpy:1378
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shin_c315e1d3:

    # "Umm, that aside everyone is...{p}Oh, underneath that parasol is Shin-kun."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3153-3154)
    "呃，每个人都要看到的话……{p}哦，伞下的那个人不是深君么。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1384
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shin_11e90be1:

    # si "「Hey.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3162)
    si "「呀啊。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1385
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shin_083cd646:

    # fn "「Huh? You're not going to swim Shin-kun?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3165)
    fn "「哈？你没有去游泳吗？深君？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1389
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shin_1e2263b3:

    # si "「I'm going to pass.{p} I don't really like getting wet.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3170-3171)
    si "「我就算了吧，{p}我不想弄得身上湿湿的。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1390
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shin_e8d4635b:

    # fn "「But we came all the way to the beach.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3174)
    fn "「但是我们大家都来沙滩了啊。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1394
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shin_44bcc04c:

    # si "「Well, if it's a shallow place,{p} then okay...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3179)
    si "「好吧，如果水不深的话，{p}我大概能接受吧……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1395
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shin_1e5bd7e9:

    # fn "「Eh?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3182)
    fn "「诶？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1399
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shin_689d3056:

    # si "「Nothing.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3187)
    si "「没什么。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1403
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shin_8879fce6:

    # "After saying that,{p}Shin-kun opened the lid of a bottle."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3191)
    "说完这话，深君打开了一个盒子的盖子。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1404
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shin_16c49652:

    # "He started rubbing a milky,{p}white cream all over himself."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3192)
    "他开始往自己身上涂白色的乳霜。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1405
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shin_f83d44a7:

    # "Some kind of sunscreen?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3193)
    "难道是某种防晒霜？"

# game/day 7.rpy:1406
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shin_72724651:

    # fn "「What's that?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3196)
    fn "「这是啥？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1407
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shin_30cf96a5:

    # si "「UV Cream.{w} Amaki insists that\n ultraviolet rays are bad for fur.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3201-3202)
    si "「UV防晒乳。{p}紫外线对皮肤是有害的，天木君一直坚持用的。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1411
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shin_13843a5f:

    # "This Amaki-san, is he someone...{p}who manages Shin-kun's household?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3204-3205)
    "这个天木，是他的什么人……{w=.3}深君的家庭里某个专门管他的长辈？"

# game/day 7.rpy:1415
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shin_12c80346:

    # si "「I don't really like this cream, though.{p} I can't see my back,{p} and I could miss a spot.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3210-3211)
    si "「说实在话，我真的不喜欢涂这种乳霜。{p}我够不到我的背，{p}这样有些地方就涂不到了。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1416
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shin_7620613b:

    # fn "「Uh-huh.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3214)
    fn "「诶，哈啊，是啊。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1417
translate chinese_simplified beach07_shin_4908cde6:

