translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_98ac9722:

    # ky "「Why don't all three of us go in together?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3923)
    ky "「为什么我们三个不一起进去换呢？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1593
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_4c714b55:

    # so "「...!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3927)
    so "「！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1594
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_5f19c5ba:

    # fn "「Whaaaat!?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3930)
    fn "「什什什什……什么！？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1595
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_83fd5d87:

    # "When Kyouji says that,{p}he has a serious look on his face."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3932-3933)
    "京慈在说这句话的时候，{p}表情十分郑重。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1596
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_66fbaa7a:

    # "He said that without any warning.{p}I shout from a strange place,{p}in the back of my throat."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3935-3937)
    "说话之前也没有任何的预兆。{p}我太过激动，{p}从喉咙深处叫出来一声连我自己都不认识的声音。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1597
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_eca8f5b8:

    # fn "「Ch-change together?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3940)
    fn "「一起…一起换？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1598
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_69de370d:

    # ky "「Yeah. Three people going separately,{p} isn't very efficient, right?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3943)
    ky "「是啊。{p}三个人分开换太慢了不是么？"

# game/day 7.rpy:1599
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_ad23f812:

    # ky "This way we won't keep the next person,{p} waiting until we're done.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3944)
    ky "而且分开换的话，我们会让后面的人等太久的。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1600
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_663a3572:

    # fn "「I-I guess so, but...{p} H-hey? Soutarou-kun.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3947-3948)
    fn "「我…我想也是吧…{p}对、{w=.3}对吧？{p}宗太郎君」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1601
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_445a20e4:

    # "I glance over at him."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3950)
    "我瞥了他一眼。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1602
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_f92faaa8:

    # "The small changing hut looks,{p}like it would be a bit crowded,{p}with 3 people inside."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3952-3953)
    "更衣室这么小，{p}三个人一起进来的话，估计会有点儿挤吧。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1603
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_aaf8d224:

    # "But above all, I'll be in an enviroment,{p}where those two will be naked,{p}only a few centimeters away."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3955-3956)
    "他们两个裸着上身，{p}离我只有一点点儿距离。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1604
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_14a7e471:

    # "I have no idea how much,{p}of that I'll be able to resist."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3957)
    "我脑袋里一片空白，都不知道手脚该往哪放。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1605
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_2647a76f:

    # "Surely Soutarou-kun,{p}must be embarrassed about this..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3959)
    "不过我猜，宗太郎也对此有些尴尬…"

# game/day 7.rpy:1609
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_9ee7a331:

    # so "「I don't see anything wrong with that...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3964-3965)
    so "「？{p}吼哈，{w=.3}{w=.3}我不觉得这有什么不对劲的地方啊……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1610
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_f706b473:

    # fn "「Wh-Whaaat!?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3969)
    fn "「什、{w=.3}什么？？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1611
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_2ff3d4cd:

    # "When Soutarou kun says that,{p}he has a serious look on his face."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3971-3972)
    "宗太郎说这话的时候。{p}脸上写满了认真。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1612
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_b3a1c131:

    # ky "「What's wrong, [fn]?{p} Your voice sounds strange.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3975-3976)
    ky "「怎么了？{w=.3}　[fn]{p}你声音听起来怪怪的呢。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1613
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_1f91a0f9:

    # fn "「N-no no! I-It's nothing!{p} You just suggested that so suddenly,{p} that it took me off guard, that's all.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3979-3980)
    fn "「没、{w=.3}没事没事！{p}能、{w=.3}能有什么事啊！{p}你突然这么说，搞得我一时没反应过来{w=.3}而已。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1614
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_0ecad9dd:

    # ky "「Is that so?{p} Anyway, let's get in.{p} We're holding those behind us up.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3983-3984)
    ky "「是这样么？{p}不管怎么说，我们赶紧换衣服吧。{p}已经让后面的人等了很久了。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1615
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_0212ea2a:

    # to "「Hey [fn], hurry up and get in there,{p} Are you gonna skip your turn?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3987-3988)
    to "「嘿，[fn]你倒是快点儿啊，{p}你还要不要换衣服啊！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1616
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_3701d286:

    # fn "「A-all right...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3991)
    fn "「好，好了，马上完了……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1617
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_724b8429:

    # "Feeling the pressure from Torahiko,{p}we finally enter the changing room."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3993-3994)
    "听到虎彦的催促，{p}最后我们三个还是一起进了更衣室。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1623
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_25a9237c:

    # "As soon as we get in,{p}Kyouji immediately begins to undress."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3999)
    "在我们进去的同时，京慈马上就开始脱衣服了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1627
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_c543599e:

    # "I hesitate once, but I can't stand it,{p}I sometimes glance over them."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4002-4003)
    "我愣了一下，{p}但是还是忍不住时不时的看看他们。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1628
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_5d9fb3cd:

    # "Huh? I'm not feeling guilty?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4005)
    "哈？{p}我居然没有内疚感？"

# game/day 7.rpy:1629
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_f22256aa:

    # "Because we're changing,{p}with our backs facing each other,{p}they won't notice."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4006-4007)
    "大概是因为我们都在换衣服，大家相互背对着，{p}……所以他们没有注意到我。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1630
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_fabf63fe:

    # "...I'll probably be safe."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4007)
    "我大概还是安全的吧。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1631
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_faf68cc5:

    # "Kyouji has a tight body,{p}while Soutarou-kun's is slender and delicate."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4009)
    "京慈的身体很紧致，宗太郎则比较修长细腻。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1632
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_9d36b622:

    # "They've trained their bodies from soccer,{p}so there's no excess fat at all."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4010-4011)
    "他们的身体已经在踢足球的时候得到锻炼了，{p}所以身上没有一丁点儿多余的脂肪。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1633
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_51de8b15:

    # "I look down at my stomach and compare.{p}...I haven't been getting much excersise lately."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4013-4014)
    "再看看我的肚腩…{p}……我已经很久没有运动了…身上已经有相当明显的赘肉。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1634
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_ad330807:

    # "Some fat is clearly showing.{p}I try pinching it with both of my hands."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4015)
    "我试着把这些赘肉挤出来，"

# game/day 7.rpy:1635
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_9dc3706c:

    # "..Just as I expected, it's gotten pretty bad."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4017)
    "……但是并没有得偿所愿，反而变的更糟了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1641
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_d45a0bd1:

    # so "「Okay, I'm ready!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4026)
    so "「好了，我换好啦！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1642
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_5228a2a1:

    # ky "「...Hm, [fn] you haven't...{p} changed yet?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4029)
    ky "「……嗯、[fn]，你还没换完么？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1643
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_b5ad05af:

    # fn "「Huh?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4032)
    fn "「啊哈？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1644
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_26d9db71:

    # "I turn my head. They're standing there,{p}already in their bathing suits.{p}Aaaah, I've failed my mission..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4034-4035)
    "我抬起头，他们已经站在那里了，早就换好了衣服。{p}啊啊啊啊啊，我又走神了……。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1645
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_185c2139:

    # so "「Oh, did you forget somethin'?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4038)
    so "「哦？你是不是忘记了什么东西了？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1646
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_00ff0b75:

    # "Soutarou-kun asks.{p}Th-this pain in my chest is too much..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4040-4041)
    "宗太郎问道。{p}我突然感到胸口略疼……。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1647
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_64487db5:

    # fn "「No, that's not it...{p} Th-that's right!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4044)
    fn "「没，没有…我没什么问题！……"

# game/day 7.rpy:1648
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_a1724859:

    # fn "My pants zipper is stuck!{p} I can't get it to go down...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4045-4046)
    fn "只，只是！{p}我的拉链坏了！{p}我拉不下来……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1649
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_065c3a08:

    # ky "「I see...{p} Well, we'll go out first.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4050)
    ky "「我明白了……{p}我们先出去吧。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1650
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_b09761e0:

    # ky "「Let's go, Tarou.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4053)
    ky "「走吧，宗。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1654
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_a13cf24e:

    # so "「Okay!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4057)
    so "「好的！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1660
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_669d8135:

    # "They put their clothes in their bags and leave."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4061)
    "他们把衣服放在包里，然后先走了，"

# game/day 7.rpy:1661
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_75ff15b9:

    # "Now it's just me left in the hut."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4063)
    "现在只剩下我一个人留在更衣室里。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1662
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_97b2c980:

    # fn "「...Anyway, shall I get changed?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4066)
    fn "「……还是说，其实是我变了？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1663
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_93a7359a:

    # "Feeling awkward, I pick up my bathing suit."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4068)
    "这么想着，我拿起我的泳衣。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1668
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_3d74f190:

    # "Finished changing, I return to the beach,{p}and I see everybody's in the water,{p}having a good time."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4075-4076)
    "换完衣服我回到了沙滩上，{p}然后我看到大家都已经下水，享受美好时光了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1669
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_db617cb6:

    # "Now where did those two go..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4078)
    "他们俩现在在哪儿呢……"

# game/day 7.rpy:1670
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_20b4feca:

    # "Ah, there they are.{p}I wave at them from the beach."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4080)
    "啊，在那儿呢。{p}我在沙滩边朝他们挥了挥手，"

# game/day 7.rpy:1671
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_d74b545f:

    # "I run straight down the sandy beach,{p}to where they are."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4081)
    "我径直朝他们跑了过去。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1677
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_f26c73f8:

    # fn "「Wait up!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4090)
    fn "「等等！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1678
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_143eb50e:

    # ky "「Good. [fn] has arrived,{p} so we can start warming up first.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4093-4094)
    ky "「好了。[fn]已经到了，{p}我们可以开始先热身了。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1679
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_2b391d1a:

    # fn "「Eh... but aren't we just swimming?{p} There's no need to warm up for that...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4097-4098)
    fn "「呃？但是我们不是来游泳的吗？{p}游泳还需要热身的吗？……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1680
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_00c78f9b:

    # ky "「Now now, [fn],{p} isn't being prepared for anything important?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4101)
    ky "「对啊，[fn]，准备工作非常重要不是么？"

# game/day 7.rpy:1681
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_cc35bbce:

    # ky "「Your opponent is the sea.{p} It's different from the pool,{p} and the river."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4102)
    ky "你的对手可是大海，不是小水池，或者小河什么的，"

# game/day 7.rpy:1682
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_0df201b3:

    # ky "So if you don't prepare,{p} there's a chance you could even drown.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4103)
    ky "如果你不做准备运动的话，你就有可能会溺水而亡了。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1683
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_49902232:

    # fn "「That's overdoing it...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4106)
    fn "「这有点儿太夸张了…」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1687
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_2d394007:

    # ju "「...No, there's a reason,{p} for Takahara's instructions.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4111)
    ju "「……不，一点都不夸张，既然高原都这么说了。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1688
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_14c722b8:

    # fn "「Whoa, Ju-Juuichi-san...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4114)
    fn "「哇啊，{w=.3}柔、{w=.3}柔一君……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1689
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_c3ca8144:

    # "At my negligent reply,{p}Juuichi-san suddenly appears from behind."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4116-4117)
    "在我马马虎虎地回答了京慈之后，{p}柔一君出现在了我的后面"

# game/day 7.rpy:1690
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_e3cfd213:

    # "I turn around and see him,{p}looking at me square in the eyes."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4119)
    "我转过身看着他，与他充满严肃的双眼对视。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1691
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_87f908ef:

    # ju "「There's no such thing as being 100%% prepared.{p} However, thanks to the act of preparation,{p} you can recognize your own inexperience.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4122-4124)
    ju "「俗话说有备无患。{p}不管怎么说，多亏了这准备工作，{p}你才能意识到自己的经验不足。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1692
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_e89426f0:

    # ju "「...Understand?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4124)
    ju "……懂了吗？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1693
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_dfa2d46a:

    # fn "「Y-yeah...{p} I'll be more diligent...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4127)
    fn "「嗯…{w=.3}是……{p}我会更加努力的……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1694
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_56810826:

    # "I give him an agreeable response,{p}then get out of his focus.{p}Whew, that was scary..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4129-4131)
    "我积极地回应着他，{p}然后从他的视线中逃离了。{p}啊，好恐怖的脸……"

# game/day 7.rpy:1695
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_6046dd2c:

    # ju "「So, I'll join in too.{p} Is that fine, Takahara?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4133-4135)
    ju "「所以，我也要加入。{p}没问题吧？{w=.3}　高原」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1696
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_0922a3bb:

    # ky "「Oh, of course it is.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4138)
    ky "「好，当然没问题了」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1700
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_b8102c6c:

    # "Then, we, along with Juuichi-san,{p}begin our warm up excercises on the beach."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4142-4143)
    "然后，我跟着柔一君，{p}在沙滩边开始了热身运动。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1701
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_5d08c6eb:

    # "In front of us, Kyouji leads the work-out."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4145)
    "京慈则在前面领着我们一起做。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1702
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_9b975a83:

    # "Since he's the captain of his club,{p}he's almost like a coach,{p}in the middle of pratice."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4146-4147)
    "不管怎么说，他是他社团的负责人，{p}在热身运动的过程中他就像大家的教练一样。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1703
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_049ffee7:

    # "The only difference,{p}is that we're in our bathing suits."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4149)
    "唯一不同的是，我们都穿着泳衣。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1704
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_807646ab:

    # "Well, we were naked together...{p}but, for now I'll let this be my motivation."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4150-4151)
    "好吧…其实我们都裸着身子…{p}但是，从现在开始我要提起干劲来！"

# game/day 7.rpy:1705
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_a20cefa7:

    # "..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4153)
    "……。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1709
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_eb445b79:

    # ka "「What's wrong, [fn]?{p} It's just a warm-up, but it looks like,{p} you're pulling your back all weird.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4158-4159)
    ka "「怎么了，[fn]。{p}只是热身运动而已，可是你干嘛这么卖力地压背。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1710
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_b4d9e63f:

    # "Looking at my posture,{p}Kouya makes fun of me from behind."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4161)
    "看着我的架势，洸哉忍不住在我身后吃吃笑了起来。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1711
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_6cf54c01:

    # fn "「Th-this is nothing!{p} Besides, you're just standing there,{p} watching, you should join us.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4163-4166)
    fn "「没…没事。{p}说起来，你只是站在那儿看，{p}你应该也跟我们一起来啊。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1715
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_fb27a502:

    # ka "「Oh, I'm fine.{p} Even if I get a cramp or anything,{p} I'm sure I'll be able to manage somehow.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4170-4172)
    ka "「哈，我没关系的。{p}就算我意外抽筋或者发生了别的什么，{p}我相信一定也有办法的。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1716
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_b9a8ed3d:

    # fn "「R-really...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4175)
    fn "「真…{w=.3}真的呢……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1717
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_81f21dfe:

    # "His arm...{p}I don't think there would be any problem."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4177-4178)
    "他健壮的胳膊…{p}对于如此壮硕的他，我想不出还有什么问题会让他溺水。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1721
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_5a69d8c6:

    # ka "「Well then, I should get back,{p} to swimming soon.{p} Good luck with the exercise.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4182-4184)
    ka "「嗯，好，就这样吧，我该回去了，一会儿下水游泳去。{p}热身运动，加油。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1725
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_77ef55c7:

    # "As he says that,{p}Kouya starts running down the beach."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4188)
    "随着他远去，"

# game/day 7.rpy:1726
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_0b8e876e:

    # "As he departs, I give him a look of envy,{p}shake away my delusions,{p}and stretch the tendons in my foot."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4189-4190)
    "我投去羡慕的目光，{p}打破自己脑海里的妄想，伸展了一下脚部肌肉。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1735
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_dc2ed2a1:

    # so "「Senpai, let's hurry up and get in!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4206)
    so "「前辈，我们快一点把热身运动做完吧！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1736
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_836f1c05:

    # ky "「Oh, come on now, Tarou.{p} Don't rush too much.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4209)
    ky "「嘿、嘿——宗。{p}别跑那么快。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1737
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_b1db64ec:

    # "We finish warming up,{p}and head straight for the water."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4211)
    "结束了热身运动，我们就开始准备下水了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1738
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_a4244e58:

    # "Soutarou-kun grabs on to Kyouji's arm,{p}and forcefully pulls him."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4212)
    "宗太郎抓着京慈的手，用力把他拉下水。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1739
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_3a84d998:

    # "First things first,{p}I get to the water's edge,{p}and try to soak my feet."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4214)
    "我先是来到水边，开始将我的脚浸湿。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1740
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_4e8b5dbc:

    # "The clear waves caress my bare feet.{p}Ah, this... feels good..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4216-4217)
    "清澈的海浪拥抱着我的脚，{p}啊！这感觉…心旷神怡。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1745
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_c7b7d2d4:

    # ky "「Hey, Tarou!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4222)
    ky "「嘿，宗！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1746
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_65204aa1:

    # "Kyouji swipes at the water's surface,{p}sending a spray of water,{p}in Soutarou-kun's direction."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4224-4225)
    "京慈用手托起水，{p}溅起水花，{p}朝宗太郎的方向泼过去。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1750
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_5c502a43:

    # so "「Waah, s-senpai, please stop!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4229-4231)
    so "「哇啊，{w=.3}前、{w=.3}前辈，{p}快停下啦！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1751
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_6d6da911:

    # "Soutarou-kun doesn't like how he's acting,{p}but he's enjoying it a little."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4233)
    "宗太郎并没有表示不满，反而很有点享受的样子。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1752
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_37849523:

    # "The sight of those two playing,{p}creates a romantic scene."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4235-4236)
    "他们玩闹的场景，在水沫的反射中飞溅着阳光的碎片，{p}看起来真浪漫呢。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1753
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_c8160ec1:

    # "D-damn... I'm jealous...{p}If those two can show off like that,{p}then I...!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4238-4239)
    "啊、{w=.3}好吧…我有点嫉妒他们了。{p}如果他们也能跟我这么玩的话，我一定…！"

# game/day 7.rpy:1757
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_70b05f31:

    # fn "「Take this!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4244)
    fn "「看招！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1761
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_8b6d9b23:

    # so "「Woah, you too, [ln]-san!?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4248)
    so "「哇啊，[西村]也过来闹啊？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1762
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_735a3851:

    # ky "「All right, Tarou!{p} Now, focus your attack on [fn]!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4250-4252)
    ky "「好吧，宗！{p}现在，把咱们的火力点对准[fn]吧！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1766
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_a13cf24e_1:

    # so "「Okay!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4256)
    so "「好！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1770
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_7fbbd487:

    # ky "「There!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4260)
    ky "「开火啦！！！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1771
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_041949f8:

    # fn "「Eh, you two are being unfair... Woah!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4263)
    fn "「啊，你们两个这样不公平…哇啊！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1772
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_74b69611:

    # "Water is splashed at me,{p}from two different directions at once."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4265)
    "同时从两个方向袭来的海水，泼得我满身都是。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1773
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_d81290e2:

    # "I-I'm being attacked by two athletes,{p}I'm clearly at a disadvantage here!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4266)
    "被两个健壮的家伙欺负了，在这里处于不利位置啊！"

# game/day 7.rpy:1774
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kyoutarou_a2c4c6d9:

    # "Frolicking around the water like this,{p}it reminds me of how,{p}we used to play in the river."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 4268-4269)
    "这样的戏水场面，让我不禁想到，{p}以前我们在河边玩耍的日子。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1789
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_b023826f:

    # "This changing room is pretty shabby,{p}but it's better than nothing.{p}I finish changing in this hut."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3439-3440)
    "这更衣室太简陋了，不过总比没有强，{p}我在里面换好了衣服。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1790
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_b9672c26:

    # "Hmm, the endless blue sky. The dazzling sun.{p}The deep blue ocean that stretches out.{p}And the scorching hot sand."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3442-3443)
    "呼啊，一望无际的湛蓝天空与耀眼的阳光，{p}大海是漫无边际的深蓝。{p}还有这广阔无垠的灼热沙滩。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1791
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_ed699e9c:

    # "Ooh, I feel like I could just cry out."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3444-3444)
    "哇哦，我感觉自己都快感动得热泪盈眶了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1795
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_bf941a4c:

    # ko "「Yahoo!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3449-3449)
    ko "「呀呼！！！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1796
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_a20cefa7:

    # "..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3451-3451)
    "……。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1797
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_03823f06:

    # "Well, I guess Kounosuke is different."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3453-3453)
    "好吧，我想孝之助{p}和以前稍微有点不一样了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1801
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_6761a6c4:

    # su "「Yahoo!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3461-3461)
    su "「呀呼！！！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1802
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_571b5539:

    # "Don't get caught up with him, Shun-kun..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3463-3463)
    "别跟他一起闹了…峻…"

# game/day 7.rpy:1803
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_8768a399:

    # "Thinking about crying out, too, for a moment,{p}but then realize it's a stupid idea.{p}I'm getting embarrassed."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3465-3467)
    "我一开始还在想着要不要也跟着他们一起吼两声发泄，{p}但是很快，我就意识到这种行为非常二。{p}有点羞耻啊。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1807
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_afa0f7a2:

    # ko "「Are you going to yell too, [fn]?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3472-3472)
    ko "「[fn]。你不跟着一起来吼两声发泄一下吗？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1811
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_f303f9b5:

    # su "「It feels good to shout!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3477-3477)
    su "「这么叫很带感啊！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1812
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_21da1163:

    # fn "「No, stop...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3480-3480)
    fn "「不要，停下来别喊了……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1818
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_4f6554ae:

    # kosu "「But it's so refreshing!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3488-3488)
    kosu "「但是这么叫真的太令人兴奋了！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1819
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_a32c9702:

    # "Don't sing in harmony."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3490-3490)
    "拜托你别跟着他一起闹了……"

# game/day 7.rpy:1820
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_d6817c38:

    # fn "「Shun-kun aside, Kounosuke,{p} you're too old to be using a swimming ring.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3493-3494)
    fn "「峻还在边上呢，{p}还有孝之助，你都这么大了，还要用泳圈。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1824
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_7634db72:

    # ko "「Huh? You don't understand.{p} Floating around the waves is comfortable.{p} Right, Shun-kun?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3499-3501)
    ko "「啊哈？{p}这你就有所不知了。{p}在海浪上漂浮可是相当舒服的{p}是吧，峻？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1828
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_76442af1:

    # su "「It is.{p} Besides, I know how to swim properly.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3506-3507)
    su "「就是就是。{p}而且，我还知道要怎样游才舒服。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1834
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_bf7493a2:

    # kosu "「That's right!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3515-3515)
    kosu "「对吧！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1835
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_5da4b05c:

    # "...Since when have you guys been buddies?{p}Well, in essence, isn't it like using a boat,{p}made for one person?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3517-3518)
    "你们两个什么时候关系变得这么好了？{p}嘛，就像是两个人共乘同一条船那样，默契非常？"

# game/day 7.rpy:1839
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_1ee6f267:

    # ko "「Why don't you get one too?{p} It gives you a resistance to the waves,{p} and it's more fun than just swimming."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3522-3524)
    ko "「[fn]为什么不也一起来呢？{p}它可以让你乘风破浪，而且这可比光游泳要有意思多啦。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1840
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_b34c3e68:

    # ko "I borrowed mine from the beach hut over there.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3522-3524)
    ko "我也把我的泳圈从更衣室拿来了」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1841
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_36afbfad:

    # fn "「Hmm. Well, I guess I'll get one too.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3527-3527)
    fn "「嗯。好吧，似乎我也该拿一个过来」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1847
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_aa149e21:

    # ko "「See you!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3534-3534)
    ko "「回见啦！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1848
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_495ba602:

    # su "「Later!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3537-3537)
    su "「待会见！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1852
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_ed0af162:

    # fn "「Oh. This is pretty nice.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3542-3542)
    fn "「喔。{p}这样很棒啊。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1853
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_182e7899:

    # "Kounosuke was right,{p}using a swim ring to float,{p}on the waves without sinking is fun."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3544-3545)
    "孝之助说的没错。{p}倚靠在泳圈上，在海浪上漂来漂去真的很有趣。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1854
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_aa1376d9:

    # "It gets in the way when I try to swim,{p}but that resistance to swimming,{p}makes it unusually interesting."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3547-3548)
    "我游泳时，泳圈会妨碍我，{p}但正是有了这种妨碍，让我感受到了一种不同寻常的趣味。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1860
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_daf69499:

    # ko "「See? It is fun, isn't it?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3559-3559)
    ko "「看吧？{p}　很有趣对吧？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1865
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_5a0ec3c6:

    # su "「Splash splash!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3563-3563)
    su "「浪花来了！浪花来了！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1866
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_57235b36:

    # "Kounosuke approaches me,{p}wearing a swimming ring as well."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3565-3565)
    "孝之助也带着泳圈，往我这边靠近。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1867
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_24209623:

    # "Shun-kun is floating a short distance away.{p}We play and splash about in the water."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3566-3567)
    "峻在不远的地方玩漂浮。{p}我们玩水、泼水，不亦乐乎。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1868
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_95e85c7c:

    # fn "「Yeah. It's pretty amusing.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3570-3570)
    fn "「是啊。{p}这样真的很有意思呢。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1872
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_de72469c:

    # ko "「Why don't we teach him about how fun this is?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3575-3575)
    ko "「为啥我们不把深也拉过来，让他也知道这是多么有趣的事咧？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1873
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_b5ad05af:

    # fn "「Huh?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3578-3578)
    fn "「？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1879
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_bef95801:

    # si "「...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3590-3590)
    si "「……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1886
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_e1fe0f3a:

    # fn "「But Shin-kun's a really bad swimmer isn't he?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3600-3600)
    fn "「但深不是个旱鸭子么？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1890
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_bb625b7d:

    # ko "「It's all right, it's all right.{p} He won't sink with a swim ring.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3605-3606)
    ko "「没事，没事。{p}他带着泳圈不会沉水里去的」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1891
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_2d84c684:

    # fn "「Eh. I think it's better if we don't.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3609-3609)
    fn "「呃。我想最好别这样了」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1892
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_a730a3e9:

    # ko "「He'll be fine.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3612-3612)
    ko "「他不会有事的啦。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1896
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_13d0af75:

    # "When Kounosuke has that face,{p}it usually means he's up to no good."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3616-3617)
    "当孝之助脸上挂着这种表情时，{p}一般都意味着他又有什么坏主意了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1897
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_be972a5b:

    # "With a touch of uneasiness,{p}I follow him to the beach."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3618-3618)
    "带着一丝不安的情绪，我跟着孝之助跑去"

# game/day 7.rpy:1903
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_bef95801_1:

    # si "「...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3628-3628)
    si "「……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1909
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_8fada7e2:

    # si "「...I have some money on me,{p} but I'm not sure how much...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3633-3633)
    si "「……这时，从黑暗中伸出来一只手」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1913
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_38754d4d:

    # ko "「Shin-kuuun.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3637-3637)
    ko "「深——」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1917
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_bb8ca19f:

    # si "「What?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3642-3642)
    si "「什么？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1918
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_0862a5ba:

    # "Shin-kun languidly raises his eyes,{p}from the paperback he was reading."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3644-3644)
    "深无精打采地从书里抬起头，揉了揉眼睛。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1922
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_0f6e7d5d:

    # ko "「Let's swim together!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3648-3648)
    ko "「我们一起去游泳吧！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1926
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_bef95801_2:

    # si "「...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3654-3654)
    si "「……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1930
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_a7870943:

    # si "「I'll pass. I don't like getting wet.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3660-3661)
    si "「放过我吧。{p}我可不想把身上弄湿。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1934
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_6f7b0e56:

    # ko "「Don't say that.{p} You can have a swim ring,{p} so you won't go underwater.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3664-3666)
    ko "「别这么说啊。{p}你拿个泳圈不就好了么，{p}这样就不会沉到水里去了。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1938
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_1ce6f41a:

    # si "「A swim ring...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3672-3672)
    si "「泳圈么……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1939
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_f659a4a6:

    # ko "「There's nothing embarrassing about it.{p} We're not at the swimming pool,{p} but you still can have one."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3675-3677)
    ko "「这没什么好羞耻的啦。{p}我们又不是在公共泳池，你可以放心地用泳圈。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1943
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_393a3595:

    # ko "Look, Shun-kun's having fun over there.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3677-3677)
    ko "你看，峻他不是玩得正开心么。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1944
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_86bcfb20:

    # si "「Even if you say that,{p} I still don't like getting wet...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3682-3683)
    si "「但是就算你这么说，{p}我还是不想把身上弄湿…」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1948
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_6fddd387:

    # ko "「Come on, we've been waiting,{p} a long time to go to the beach.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3688-3689)
    ko "「来嘛来嘛，我们都期待了很久才来沙滩的不是么。{p}深也一起来吧。{w=.3}呐？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1952
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_4d9ccbd0:

    # si "「Wait a minute Kounosuke!{p} My book is getting wet.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3694-3694)
    si "「等等，孝之助！{p}　我的书湿掉了啦！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1956
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_03d1e610:

    # ko "「Then hurry up and put it down.{p} Let's get in the water and swim!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3698-3699)
    ko "「那就赶紧把书放下，{p}我们一块下水游泳去！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1957
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_a4a481fb:

    # si "「What!? Don't pull on me!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3702-3702)
    si "「你在干什么！？{w=.3}别……{w=.3}别拉着我啊！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1964
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_9fc87688:

    # ko "「See, isn't rocking in the waves fun?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3710-3710)
    ko "「看吧，在水里摇摆很有意思不是么？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1970
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_c356aea5:

    # si "「Y-yeah...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3714-3714)
    si "「是…{w=.3}是吧……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1971
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_c6315c6d:

    # ko "「Let's go away from the beach,{p} where it's deeper.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3717-3717)
    ko "「我们游得离沙滩远一点，到深一点儿地方去」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1972
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_a60f6550:

    # si "「Sto-wait!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3720-3720)
    si "「停…下来…{w=.3}等……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1977
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_757c0919:

    # "Kounosuke swims behind Shin-kun,{p}and pushes on his swim ring."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3725-3725)
    "孝之助在深的后面游着，并将他的泳圈向前推。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1978
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_f4c52814:

    # "Naturally, this causes him,{p}to go towards the open sea."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3726-3726)
    "很自然地，孝之助的推力让他向着更广的海域游去了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1979
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_f546b048:

    # si "「Kounosuke! D-don't grab my foot!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3729-3729)
    si "「孝之助！{p}　不、{w=.3}不要拽我的脚！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1980
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_676c202c:

    # ko "「Look, splash, splash!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3732-3732)
    ko "「看，浪花过来了！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1981
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_283437ef:

    # si "「N-no! Sto-stop it!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3735-3735)
    si "「别、{w=.3}别这样…{p}停下…{w=.3}你快停下…」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1982
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_b492aee6:

    # "Shin-kun's shouting gets gradually weaker."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3737-3737)
    "深的叫声越来越弱。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1986
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_6bacbc35:

    # si "「K-Kounosuke.{p} T-take me back already.{p} Kouno...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3743-3744)
    si "「孝、{w=.3}孝之助。{p}够、{w=.3}够了，{w=.3}快回去…{p}孝之……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1987
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_2e952376:

    # "Then, Shin-kun looks like,{p}he sees what's coming."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3746-3746)
    "然后，深注意到了在自己身后，{p}"

# game/day 7.rpy:1988
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_39a2b557:

    # "Kounosuke pushes harder,{p}than he means to on his swim ring,{p}and disappears before I know it."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3747-3748)
    "那个正将自己的泳圈推向浪花的孝之助。{p}那是他们消失之后，我才知道的事。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1989
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_a488ed74:

    # "Even thought it looks like the open sea,{p}the depth is only a little less than one meter."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3750-3750)
    "即使是看起来很深很广的海域，其实也不到一米深。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1990
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_b518e031:

    # "This is usually a place,{p}where your feet can touch the bottom."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3751-3751)
    "这种深度的话，完全可以用脚轻松地踩到水底，根本不用担心。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1991
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_9b43450b:

    # "It seems his swim ring,{p}gets away from him for a little bit."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3752-3752)
    "看起来深的泳圈似乎已经离他有点远了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1992
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_299e0be0:

    # "I think he's all right but Shin-kun...{p}doesn't move an inch.{p}Worried, I approach him."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3754-3756)
    "我以为他没什么不正常的，但是深他…{p}他没有再向前移动哪怕一点点。{p}我担心地靠了过去。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1993
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_2f77e505:

    # fn "「Shin-kun?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3759-3759)
    fn "「深君？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1994
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_136dc095:

    # si "「[fn]... h-help me.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3762-3762)
    si "「[fn]……{p}帮…{w=.3}帮帮我。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1995
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_f4dc624f:

    # "He grabs tightly on to his swim ring, shaking.{p}The usually cool Shin-kun has teary eyes,{p}and asks me for help in a trembling voice."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3764-3766)
    "他紧紧抓住自己的泳圈，哆嗦着。{p}平时冷漠得拒人于千里之外的深，{p}现在正满眼泪水，用颤抖的声音求我帮忙。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1996
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_dd6ee6f1:

    # fn "「Y-you'll be okay.{p} It's not that deep.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3769-3769)
    fn "「没…{w=.3}没关系的啦。{p}这里没那么深的。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1997
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_b49c31d2:

    # si "「I-impossible...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3772-3772)
    si "「不…我…{w=.3}不可能做到的…」"

# game/day 7.rpy:1998
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_82dd034c:

    # "Shin-kun shakes his head and talks,{p}in a barely audible voice.{p}Th-this is scary."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3774-3775)
    "深摇着头说道，声音小得几乎听不到。{p}看、{w=.3}看起来他是真的很害怕。"

# game/day 7.rpy:1999
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_5aeaf828:

    # "Still, he's not where it's deep enough,{p}to go over his head."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3776-3776)
    "但是，他所站的地方根本没有那么深，至少水不会没过他的头。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2004
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_324e4db6:

    # si "「Wah.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3782-3782)
    si "「哇啊…」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2005
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_ddeb324b:

    # "His swim ring is losing balance,{p}and it looks like,{p}he's standing on the water."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3784-3786)
    "也许是因为重心压偏了，泳圈失去了平衡，{p}看起来就像是在水面上直竖着一样。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2006
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_0f7444eb:

    # si "「H-hur-hurry.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3789-3789)
    si "「快、{w=.3}快点…{w=.3}快点…」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2007
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_a122cb5c:

    # "As though he's clinging to a flying donut,{p}he gets back to his original position,{p}and I pull him back to the beach."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3791-3797)
    "已经恐慌了一半的深君胡乱地挣扎着。{p}简直就像是一只竭力抓住漂浮在空中的甜甜圈、拼了命也不肯掉下来的黑猫一样。{p}看着深君那狼狈不堪的样子，我心中涌起一种说不上来的感觉，帮他把泳圈扶正，然后拉着他回到了岸边。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2016
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_b67e53e8:

    # ko "「Err-sorry, sorry.{p} My hand slipped a little.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3808-3809)
    ko "「呃，对不起，对不起，{p}我手滑了一下。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2017
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_bef95801_3:

    # si "「...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3812-3812)
    si "「……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2021
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_d8a13842:

    # ko "「Shin?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3817-3817)
    ko "「深？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2028
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_fca3b277:

    # si "{size=+30}「IDIOT!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3824-3824)
    si "「笨蛋！！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2034
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_6d59b82b:

    # "Shin-kun runs off, crying."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3832-3832)
    "深大哭着，跑开了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2038
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_2cdafb96:

    # ko "「...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3837-3837)
    ko "「……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2039
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_be477f4b:

    # fn "「...Kounosuke, will you give him\n a better apology later?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3840-3840)
    fn "「……孝之助，你待会儿能给他好好道个道歉吗？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2043
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_4a6dc703:

    # ko "「Y-yeah...{p} ...I was just joking around a little.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3844-3845)
    ko "「嗯、{w=.3}好的。{p}……我只是跟他开个小玩笑而已。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2044
translate chinese_simplified beach07_kounosuke_a124a4ad:

    # "A little, huh?{p}That's still not a good reason."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 3847-3848)
    "只是一个过分的小玩笑而已么？{p}这并不是什么好的道歉理由啊，这只狸猫。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2052
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_08c8fbbc:

    # "...{p}It's no good, Juuichi-san is avoiding me.\nI'd better hang out with someone else today."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1717-1718)
    "不行，还是不跟柔一君说话了吧。{p}今天和别的人一起玩吧。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2064
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_f159f658:

    # "The blue sea! White clouds!{p}And the shining sun!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1732)
    "湛蓝的大海！{p}洁白的云彩！{p}阳光明媚啊！"

# game/day 7.rpy:2065
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_c6cf6d16:

    # "The weather today is just right for the beach.{p}For no reason, I nod my head."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1733-1734)
    "……今天这种天气真是适合来海边玩啊。{p}不知不觉的，我点了点头。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2066
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_85472da7:

    # "The water's surface brilliantly glitters,{p}from the reflected rays of the sun."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1736)
    "阳光打在水面上，海面波光荡漾。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2067
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_25f3c1a8:

    # "In the open water I see the yacht,{p}that we saw from the bus."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1737)
    "在海上，我看到了我们在巴士上就看到的游艇。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2068
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_f40c01f4:

    # "On the sandy beach,{p}families leisurely collect shellfish."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1738)
    "在软绵绵的沙滩上，一家人在悠闲地捡着贝壳。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2069
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_8ba185d4:

    # fn "「Now, let's have fun today!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1744)
    fn "「今天，大家一定要好好玩呐！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2070
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_d63a9409:

    # "Oh! As if to say that,{p}I cheerfully thrust my right hand to the sky."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1746-1747)
    "哦——一边这样说着，{p}我一边激动地向天空中冲出右手。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2074
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_7fe1121e:

    # ju "「...Before that, help me find\n a place to put the luggage.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1755)
    ju "「……在那之前，先帮我找个能放行李的地方吧。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2075
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_f63305da:

    # "Suddenly, Juuichi-san's face appears at my side."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1757)
    "突然间，柔一君的大脸出现在我面前，"

# game/day 7.rpy:2076
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_ddf6286d:

    # "As he says that,{p}he looks around the area restlessly,{p}it seem there's no other choice besides me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1758-1759)
    "他一边说着，一边环顾四周，{p}好像除了我，他再找不到其他人能帮忙了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2077
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_ed8bacf1:

    # "...That's weird.{p}I thought everybody was there just now."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1761-1762)
    "……真奇怪……{p}大家都跑哪去了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2078
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_71190060:

    # fn "「Oh, where's everybody else?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1765)
    fn "「呃，大家都跑哪去了？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2082
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_9a529b95:

    # ju "「...They left their bags behind,{p} and went to change.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1770)
    ju "「……他们把行李扔在了这里，然后就去换衣服了。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2083
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_4c6af77a:

    # fn "「What!?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1773)
    fn "「诶！？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2084
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_9cd1dc9f:

    # "So that means Juuichi-san is settling with me?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1775)
    "所以说这里就剩下我和柔一了？"

# game/day 7.rpy:2085
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_e5f6f7cb:

    # "I painfully understand\nthat feeling of wanting to go play,{p}but everybody just impatiently left."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1776-1777)
    "我痛苦地理解体会到那种心情，{p}迫不及待地想去玩，但是其他人却都更加迫不及待地离开了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2086
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_68a71b1e:

    # "Usually we're like a big family."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1779)
    "一般情况下，我们这儿还真像一个大家庭，"

# game/day 7.rpy:2087
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_61e0e2e2:

    # "With just two of us working,{p}I'll collapse from exhaustion\nbefore I can have fun."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1780-1781)
    "总是有两个人是干活的。{p}我想在我能去玩之前，一定会累垮的。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2091
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_a82949c4:

    # ju "「...Well, let's do it.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1786)
    ju "「……那，咱们也开始干吧。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2092
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_783aca4c:

    # fn "「Are you serious?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1789)
    fn "「你确定？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2093
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_9e955ec3:

    # ju "「There's no use in relying,{p} on those who are not there.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1792)
    ju "「求人不如求己，更何况是现在这种情形。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2094
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_c93b7d94:

    # "Ooh, do I not have any choice...?{p}I don't want to pointlessly waste my summer,{p}I should just quickly go and change my clothes."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1794-1796)
    "噢，真的没有选择了么……？{p}我可不想这样漫无目的的浪费我的暑假，{p}我真应该早早的去换衣服。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2098
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_d88b65d6:

    # ju "「...Are you running away?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1800)
    ju "「……你难道想逃跑么？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2099
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_5a9c4957:

    # "Juuichi-san puts his hand on my shoulder,{p}and looks into my eyes."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1802)
    "柔一把手搭在我的肩上，看着我的眼睛。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2100
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_d0284730:

    # "...Ooh, okay, I understand.{p}I sigh and look at all the bags,{p}that have been left there."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1803-1809)
    "……哦，好吧，我知道了……{p}我失望地检视着留在这儿所有的包。{p}我们干了好多事，比如铺开沙滩席，"

# game/day 7.rpy:2106
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_080310ee:

    # "We do various things like spread out the beach mat,{p}and we put together three umbrellas."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1810)
    "以及撑起了三把阳伞。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2107
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_adde9aa7:

    # "I blow into the swim rings,{p}and rubber boat, until I'm about to die."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1811)
    "我吹起了一个游泳圈和一个充气艇，"

# game/day 7.rpy:2108
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_729902fd:

    # "After a full 15 minutes,{p}we finally complete our base...{p}Err... place to put our luggage."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1812-1817)
    "吹到要断气了。{p}整整15分钟后，我们终于完成了我们的基地……{p}呃……只是用来放行李用的。{p}……我还没来得及游泳，就已经汗流浃背了……"

# game/day 7.rpy:2109
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_33b3173e:

    # "...I'm dripping with sweat,{p}before I even get to swim.{p}It's a good thing I brought an extra shirt."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1818-1821)
    "还好我多带了一件衬衫。{p}柔一也满身是汗，{p}他胸前已然汗透了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2110
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_03a617d5:

    # "Juuichi-san is also extremely sweaty,{p}his chest is soaked with sweat."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1823)
    "当我用袖子擦去脑门上的汗时，"

# game/day 7.rpy:2111
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_890d34b6:

    # "While wiping my forehead with the arm of my t-shirt,{p}Kouya, who had just changed into his bathing suit,{p}leisurely calls out to us."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1824)
    "洸哉恰好换好了泳衣，悠闲地向我们喊道，"

# game/day 7.rpy:2115
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_5a635fa4:

    # ka "「Oh, it's already done?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1829)
    ka "「哦，都干完了么？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2116
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_00b00233:

    # fn "「...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1832)
    fn "「……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2117
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_5d541b46:

    # "I give Kouya a scornful gaze.{p}{nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1834-1835)
    "我轻蔑地瞪着他。{p}他立即避开了我的眼睛。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2119
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_bb9a2b6c:

    # extend "His eyes immediately stare off in another direction.{p}He had this planned out from the beginning, didn't he?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1836)
    extend "……他是一开始就计划好了！？这只是他计划中的一环？"

# game/day 7.rpy:2120
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_165f695d:

    # "Just according to plan."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1836-1838)
    "……他是一开始就计划好了！？这只是他计划中的一环？{p}可恶，{w=.3}马上，{w=.3}斩！"

# game/day 7.rpy:2124
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_b8cd2eac:

    # su "「Wow, the floats are already filled up!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1843)
    su "「哇，气艇都吹好了啊！！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2125
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_d39ab7bc:

    # "I take a stance to give Kouya,{p}his well-deserved punishment,{p}but Shun-kun runs up from behind."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1845-1846)
    "我想给洸哉一个应得的惩罚。{p}但是峻从后面跑了上来，"

# game/day 7.rpy:2126
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_12301fd9:

    # "Crestfallen, I collapse from exhaustion."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1847)
    "于是我放弃了，我真是累垮了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2127
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_3f874862:

    # "Shun-kun sets his butt,{p}right into the center of the swim ring,{p}and shouts with delight."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1849-1850)
    "峻一屁股扎进了游泳圈里，{p}高兴地叫着。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2128
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_77d48335:

    # "...That destructive power is tremendous."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1852-1853)
    "……这真具有杀伤性啊……{p}我移开视线，吸着鼻子，望着天，"

# game/day 7.rpy:2129
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_afdee318:

    # "I look away and supress my nosebleed,{p}by pinching my nose,{p}and looking up at the sky."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1854)
    "来阻止那流淌的鼻血。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2133
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_e0f3eca5:

    # si "「Good work, both of you.{p} We saw you over here, hurry up and get changed.{p} There's an old changing room over there."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1859-1861)
    si "「你们俩干得不错么。{p}我们大老远的就看到你们在忙了，赶快换衣服吧。{p}那里有间很旧的更衣室。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2134
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_3da6939f:

    # "Shin-kun, who is also in his bathing suit,{p}urges us to get changed."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1860-1861)
    "我们大老远的就看到你们在忙了，赶快换衣服吧。{p}那里有间很旧的更衣室。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2135
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_6a097af8:

    # "Althought I frown,{p}he's probably saying that,{p}because of our heavy sweating."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1863-1866)
    "穿着泳衣的深，在叫我们去换衣服。{p}我仔细想了想，他之所以这样说，{p}大概是因为看到了我们都汗透了的缘故吧。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2140
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_41578a47:

    # ju "「We should.{p} ...Let's go.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1875)
    ju "「说的也是。{p}……走吧」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2141
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_6eea5610:

    # "Saying that, Juuichi-san briskly walks away,{p}with a full set of clothes."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1877-1878)
    "说着，柔一迅速地走开了，{p}拿着一整套衣服。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2142
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_d24e2e70:

    # fn "「Oh, wait up Juuichi-san!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1881)
    fn "「哎，柔一君，等一下！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2143
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_bb3eda63:

    # "I chase after him from behind in a hurry.{p}Then, talk to Juuichi-san along side him."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1883-1884)
    "我赶快追上了他，{p}这样就好和他说话了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2148
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_a51fe2ce:

    # fn "「Do you have any idea,{p} where the changing room is?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1892)
    fn "「你知不知道，更衣室在哪？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2152
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_99c81e98:

    # ju "「...It's probably that.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1897)
    ju "「……应该是那个吧」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2153
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_4bd96998:

    # "He points his finger straight ahead.{p}That causes me to look ahead."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1899-1900)
    "他亮出一个指头指向前方，我便顺着看过去。{p}正如深所说，那里有一间标着「更衣室」的小屋，"

# game/day 7.rpy:2154
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_ca0a82d1:

    # "It's just like Shin-kun said,{p}there stands a changing room in name only,{p}as it's more like a dilapidated hut."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1901)
    "它看起来破得快不行了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2155
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_39f08e21:

    # fn "「It sure is run-down.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1904)
    fn "「我觉得它已经荒废了。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2156
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_25abb8be:

    # ju "「It's better than nothing.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1907)
    ju "「总比没有好。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2157
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_9b8d5411:

    # "While talking, Juuichi-san and I,{p}enter the changing room."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1909)
    "说着，我和柔一君走了进去。"

# game/day 7.rpy:2161
translate chinese_simplified beach07_juuichi_11a937f3:

    # "I look around inside.{p}There are shelves to temporarily put your stuff on."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 1913-1914)
