translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_9ec0ac30:

    # to "「Oh, I'm getting a good feeling about those waves.{p} These are perfect surfing conditions.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 909-911)
    to "「哦，这浪感觉还真不错啊，{p} 这是冲浪的绝佳状态」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2995
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_40da44a3:

    # fn "「Hey, show me how to do it first.{p} I want to see how it's done.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 913-915)
    fn "「呐，你先示范一下给我看看啊。{p} 我想看看你的身手」"

# game/day 7.rpy:2996
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_9fec999b:

    # to "「Okay, leave it to me!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 917-918)
    to "「OK，交给我吧！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3000
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_42a72115:

    # "He says as he plunges into the sea,{p}splashing about as he swims."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 920-922)
    "话还没说完，虎彦就跳入海中， 向着浪潮滑动着双手。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3001
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_dd700373:

    # "He swims fairly far away,{p}then stops, and faces me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 923-924)
    "他游得有点远的时候，停下来转向我，"

# game/day 7.rpy:3002
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_00654b38:

    # "Is that the signal he's starting?{p}He displays a great wave on his hand."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 925-926)
    "这是不是他要开始了的信号呢？ 我看到他在那使劲地摇着手。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3003
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_2abc55ce:

    # "He puts his stomach on the board then gently paddles,{p}while watching the waves intently."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 928-929)
    "他趴在冲浪板上然后慢慢地开始划水， 同时专心地看着海浪。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3004
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_c0b52290:

    # "A decent-sized wave,{p}begins a steady approach.{p}Nimbly, Torahiko stands up on his board."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 931-932)
    "一波合适的浪平稳地打了过来， 虎彦灵敏地爬起站在了冲浪板上。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3005
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_1377bdcd:

    # fn "(It looks a little awkward,{p}but it must feel pretty good,{p}to ride a wave.)"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 934-936)
    fn "「（看上去有点笨拙。 不过，乘得相当好）」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3006
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_733eaf76:

    # "While drawing an S-shaped curve as he moves,{p}a sharp spray of water flies up into the air.{p}This is really cool."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 938-940)
    "虎彦操纵着冲浪板前进着，划出一道S形的路线， 一大股海浪被急剧地溅起来，在空中飞扬， 这真的好酷啊。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3007
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_37b4270c:

    # "On his way back to the beach,{p}Torahiko lowers his foot into the water,{p}and returns with a splash."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 942-943)
    "当靠近岸边的时候，虎彦把脚踏入水中， 又溅起一波浪花。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3011
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_b9a694b7:

    # to "「It's been a while,{p} but that was pretty good!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 945-947)
    to "「虽然已经很长时间没有玩了，不过还是挺上手的！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3012
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_f56eee43:

    # fn "「That was amazing.{p} I honestly didn't think,{p} you were that good at it.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 949-951)
    fn "「好厉害啊！{p} 老实说，我都不知道你竟然玩得那么好」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3013
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_1dd3c028:

    # to "「Heh, heh, I'm not that great!{p} Well then, [fn],{p} why don't you try it right now?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 953-956)
    to "「嘿嘿，没有啦！{p} 那么，[fn]，你现在也来试试吧」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3014
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_abab42d9:

    # fn "「R-right now?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 958-959)
    fn "「……现，{w=.3}现在吗？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3015
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_6e3d4837:

    # to "「Yeah, that way you too shall know,{p} the joy of surfing.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 961-964)
    to "「嗯，我也想让[fn] 了解冲浪的乐趣啊！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3016
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_89544443:

    # fn "「...Wait a minute,{p} let me take a deep breath.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 966-967)
    fn "「……等等，先让我做个深呼吸」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3017
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_a9e5ffae:

    # "Now it's my turn.{p}Despite that awesome preformance,{p}I'm still nervous."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 969-971)
    "当轮到我的时候，尽管冲浪看上去很威风，但是我还是很紧张。 离上次去海边玩隔了好久了……{p} 而且，刚才虎彦也游得很远……"

# game/day 7.rpy:3018
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_c57af1e0:

    # "It's been a long time since,{p}I've been to the beach itself...{p}And Torahiko swam pretty far out there..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 970-971)
    "离上次去海边玩隔了好久了……{p} 而且，刚才虎彦也游得很远……"

# game/day 7.rpy:3019
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_bf5863af:

    # "As I'm thinking,{p}the sand which was so pleasant up until now,{p}becomes cold."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 973-974)
    "在我思考的同时， 刚刚还感觉十分舒服的冰凉凉的沙滩"

# game/day 7.rpy:3020
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_0e1ab618:

    # "It seems as if the sea\nis trying to drag me in.\nMy legs freeze up all on their own."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 975-977)
    "突然就好像要把自己拖入海里一样， 不由得脚都蜷曲了！"

# game/day 7.rpy:3024
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_44b4074a:

    # to "「Just stick with me.{p} You'll feel better once I show you,{p} how simple it is.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 979-982)
    to "「我会扶着你的。{p} 先从简单的开始试试吧，放心！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3025
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_8dbf9b36:

    # fn "「O-okay...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 984-985)
    fn "「好，{w=.3}好吧……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3026
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_fb912e05:

    # "I-I shouldn't be afraid.{p}I won't get anywhere,{p}if I don't step forward."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 987-988)
    "害怕也无济于事。{p} 如果不迈出脚步的话，哪里也去不了……"

# game/day 7.rpy:3027
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_232f0fc9:

    # "Anyway, with great concentration,{p}I begin to swim using the board."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 990-990)
    "总之，我静下心来利用板子游了起来。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3031
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_ff381811:

    # to "「Oh hey hey hey!{p} Are you using that as a kick board?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 992-995)
    to "「噢，{w=.3}喂喂喂！{p} 哪有人把冲浪板代替游泳板来游泳的啊？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3035
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_9075d551:

    # to "「First, make sure to not open your legs,{p} when swimming on the board."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 997-1000)
    to "「首先，要注意在板子上游泳的时候不能张开双脚， 然后，向前看，放松」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3036
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_9931970c:

    # to "Then just look straight ahead and relax.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1000-1000)
    to "「然后，向前看，放松」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3037
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_7e855ae9:

    # "I-I'm fine...{p}I'm absolutely fine..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1002-1002)
    "没，{w=.3}没关系……{p}绝对没问题……"

# game/day 7.rpy:3038
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_70d130cb:

    # "I fell off the board several times,{p}but I was somehow able,{p}to get to the open water."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1005-1006)
    "虽然途中好几次从板子上掉下来， 但总算到达了浪的面前。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3039
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_c12bbf7e:

    # "Still, because I have someone next to me,{p}someone like Torahiko, I feel quite calm."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1008-1009)
    "果然身边有人在， 我会感到很安心呢。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3040
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_c08c9f45:

    # fn "「S-so how do I do this?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1011-1012)
    fn "「我，{w=.3}我现在该做什么？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3041
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_afb2f9e6:

    # "I should only rely on Torahiko's lecture.{p}I'll try to do what I'm told."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1014-1015)
    "总之先好好听着虎彦的讲解，{p} 按照吩咐的去做吧。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3042
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_30edf1e0:

    # to "「First you wait for a wave,{p} while paddling around,{p} on the sides of the board."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1017-1019)
    to "「首先，一边划着一边等到海浪过来，」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3043
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_5bd1b2c0:

    # to "When you see a wave,{p} that you've got a good feeling about,{p} stand up quick!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1019-1020)
    to "「首先，一边划着一边等到海浪过来，{p} 如果感觉乘得不错时，就立马站起来！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3044
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_18c9c96b:

    # to "Then, give a gutsy yell or something.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1021-1021)
    to "「然后就是气势和毅力什么的。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3045
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_8cefc1e3:

    # "What does he mean by 'or something'...?{p}Even if I get into an aggressive state,{p}I'll still be worried."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1023-1024)
    "什么的是什么啊？……{p} 到这里突然发动大致模式，有没有搞错啊！"

# game/day 7.rpy:3046
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_be67ff80:

    # fn "「I don't understand your explanation.{p} A beginner like me can't just...{p} catch a wave right away, can he!?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1026-1028)
    fn "「这种谁听得懂啊？{p} 像我这样的新手怎么可能上来就可以乘上浪啊！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3050
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_88f1311a:

    # to "「Just watch me.{p} If I can do it, you can too!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1030-1033)
    to "「看我是怎么做的。{p} 只要跟我做的一样，[fn]也可以的！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3051
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_61435e85:

    # fn "「W-wait, hey Torahiko!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1035-1036)
    fn "「等，{w=.3}等等，喂，虎彦！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3055
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_881c25f6:

    # "As he says that,{p}Torahiko gallantly rides a wave."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1038-1039)
    "说完，虎彦英姿飒爽地骑上了一波浪。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3059
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_bf218a1e:

    # "Leaving me alone in the vast sea."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1041-1042)
    "留下我在这宽广的海中凌乱着。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3060
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_6421e501:

    # "Is it just my imagination,{p}or does it feel like I'm...{p}gradually being swept away?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1044-1045)
    "错觉吗？ 感觉好像渐渐被冲向浪的那边去了"

# game/day 7.rpy:3061
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_a5bf05db:

    # "Crap, this is way people drown to death."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1047-1047)
    "糟了，这是溺死Flag。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3062
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_b29e5e6d:

    # "Feeling my fear building up,{p}I ask Torahiko for help,{p}by wildly waving my hand around."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1049-1050)
    "一股恐惧从我心底涌出， 我用力的挥动双手向虎彦求助。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3063
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_247c1970:

    # "On the shore,{p}Torahiko doesn't gets what I mean,{p}and waves back obliviously."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1052-1053)
    "在岸边，虎彦却不明白我的意思， 也朝着我挥着双手。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3064
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_7d62d6bf:

    # to "「Yo! [fn]!{p} You hurry up and get back here too!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1055-1056)
    to "「喂——[fn]——你也快点过来啊————！！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3065
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_a5e750cd:

    # "Damn, this is bad isn't it?{p}I guess it doesn't matter,{p}I'll try it!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1058-1060)
    "可恶！这下糟了！{p} 总之不管怎么样，还是去试试吧！{p} 我照着自己从虎彦示范时所看到的来做……"

# game/day 7.rpy:3066
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_34a9d571:

    # "I'll just do what I saw Torahiko do..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1060-1060)
    "我照着虎彦示范时所看到的来做……"

# game/day 7.rpy:3067
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_94188ecc:

    # "Without any feeling,{p}I get on the board and wait for a wave."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1062-1063)
    "我静下心来， 爬上冲浪板等着海浪的袭来。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3068
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_6e10091f:

    # "I hope I can get up quick enough,{p}when I meet the wave."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1065-1067)
    "当乘上浪时，希望我能快速地站起来。{p} 嗯，刚刚虎彦好像是两只脚一瞬间就站起来了。{p} 然后，气势……"

# game/day 7.rpy:3069
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_ea33e56c:

    # "I mean, Torahiko got up,{p}on his feet so suddenly.{p}And then after that, he yelled out..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1066-1067)
    "嗯，刚刚虎彦好像是两只脚一瞬间就站起来了。{p}然后，气势……"

# game/day 7.rpy:3070
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_a6a6addb:

    # "In the meantime,{p}my body suddenly rises gently."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1069-1069)
    "正想着，我的身体就已经开始慢慢上浮了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3071
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_c9e92111:

    # fn "(Oh, a wave I have a good feeling about...?)"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1071-1072)
    fn "「（哦，这个浪刚刚好……？）」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3072
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_76c810c4:

    # "It's already gotten here!{p}I desperately try to recall,{p}the visual image of Torahiko standing."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1074-1077)
    "不管这么多了! {p} 我开始回忆虎彦站起来的时候的景象， 想想应该是用双脚把身体支撑起来。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3073
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_80de1b40:

    # "I draw my feet in towards my body,{p}in order to get myself standing."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1075-1077)
    "我开始回忆虎彦站起来的时候的景象， 想想应该是用双脚把身体支撑起来。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3074
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_aa842f7d:

    # "The board gradually increases height,{p}as it's being washed away by the wave."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1078-1078)
    "冲浪板被浪向前冲，并慢慢地抬高了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3075
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_c8d47969:

    # "I stand up on the board,{p}and let the momentum take me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1080-1081)
    "趁着这股势头， 我在板子上站了起来。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3076
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_de1a3b4d:

    # fn "(Huh, I'm... standing?)"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1083-1084)
    fn "「（啊咧，我……{p}站起来了？）」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3077
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_40d49cc6:

    # "For a moment I think I am, at least.{p}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1086-1086)
    "在这么想的同时，"

# game/day 7.rpy:3078
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_97be8510:

    # "The wave rapidly gets higher.{p}to the point where it springs up,{p}to a white cap."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1087-1087)
    "波浪涨的更高了，溅起了白色的浪花。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3079
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_efa3c9b1:

    # "It sends my body into the air."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1088-1088)
    "此时，我感觉自己飞向了空中。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3087
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_d46e7967:

    # "I'm violently jostled by the wave,{p}with no idea of what's going on."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1091-1092)
    "我被海浪激烈的冲击着，在什么都不知道的情况下， 等回过神来时就发现我已经在沙滩上了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3088
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_cb5c26bd:

    # "The next thing I know,{p}I find myself lying face-up on the beach."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1091-1092)
    "我被海浪激烈的冲击着，在什么都不知道的情况下， 等回过神来时就发现我已经在沙滩上了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3092
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_53d42d5b:

    # to "「Awesome, [fn]!{p} That was quite the wave to go against,{p} for your first time surfing.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1095-1097)
    to "「好厉害啊，[fn]！{p} 第一次就去挑战那种浪」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3093
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_f46c133a:

    # fn "「Torahiko...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1099-1100)
    fn "「虎彦——」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3097
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_ba693a7a:

    # to "「W-what?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1103-1104)
    to "「怎，{w=.3}怎么了？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3098
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_fe081c92:

    # fn "「Surfing is impossible for me.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1106-1107)
    fn "「冲浪对我来说，不行啊——！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3102
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_556dd0c8:

    # to "「Eh, what's with you all of a sudden?!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1110-1111)
    to "「呃？怎么突然这样说？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3103
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_14f4f7f1:

    # fn "「I just don't have the talent...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1113-1114)
    fn "「我没有那种天赋」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3104
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_809bb1ef:

    # to "「Really?{p} Didn't you think it was totally cool?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1116-1118)
    to "「是吗?{p} 你刚才做的很好啊?」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3105
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_00b00233:

    # fn "「...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1120-1121)
    fn "「……………………」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3106
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_57f54678:

    # "I wasn't blessed with a coach...{p}I think about saying that sarcastically.{p}...Nah."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1123-1125)
    "我本想指责下没遇到好教练什么的， 嘲讽几句。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3107
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_94198983:

    # "When Torahiko looks at my face,{p}he looks pretty dissapointed,{p}so I decided to keep that in mind."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1126-1128)
    "但是虎彦看着我的 那表情透露着一丝落寞， 所以我就把这话咽了回去。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3108
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_61f4d657:

    # "I see an untarnished boyishness,{p}in his eyes that clears away,{p}any anger or resentment."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1130-1131)
    "看着虎彦那天真无邪的孩子般的眼睛， 不满和愤怒都随风散去了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3109
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_24dfd39d:

    # "I think Torahiko was planning on teaching me.{p}He's a guy who goes with what he feels,{p}literally, instead of logic..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1133-1134)
    "虎彦刚才教的那些其实也有好好教的， 只不过他不是凭道理而是凭感觉去做的。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3110
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_e9dc5c13:

    # "But I can't do that."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1136-1136)
    "但是我做不到啊……"

# game/day 7.rpy:3114
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_8e614c79:

    # "While staring out at the ocean,{p}I suddenly see somebody riding a board,{p}heading this way."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1139-1140)
    "转眼向远方的海面看去， 突然看见有人在站在冲浪板上，向这边冲来。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3115
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_7be0d202:

    # "A silver gray body shines,{p}as he rides a wave,{p}creating a pure white splash of water."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1141-1141)
    "银灰色的身体让人感觉是站在在海浪上一样， 溅出来纯白色的浪花。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3116
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_d9465cee:

    # fn "(It's Kouya...)"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1143-1144)
    fn "「（是洸哉啊……）」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3117
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_a0d8ae81:

    # "He doesn't make any unecessary movements,{p}as he rides the wave."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1146-1146)
    "轻松的在海浪上滑行着，丝毫没有多余的动作。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3118
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_8de0e90b:

    # "As Kouya approaches the shore,{p}he draws a big U-shaped curve with his board,{p}making a huge spray of water splash at Torahiko."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1148-1149)
    "当靠近岸边的时候，画了一个大大U字形， 弄得一大泼水花冲向了虎彦。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3123
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_0e2945ae:

    # to "「Bwah!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1152-1153)
    to "「哇啊！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3124
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_991b47db:

    # "The spray forcefully hits Torahiko in the face,{p}causing him to spit out salty water."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1155-1156)
    "水花直接打在了虎彦的脸上， 弄得虎彦一脸狼狈，使劲地吐着海水。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3131
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_58ef8dba:

    # ka "「Yo.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1163-1164)
    ka "「哟！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3132
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_4c93c5e1:

    # fn "「Amazing!{p} You're also a great surfer, aren't you?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1166-1167)
    fn "「好厉害啊！{p} 洸哉也很会冲浪嘛」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3136
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_913c3286:

    # ka "「What do you mean by 'also'?{p} Sorry, we're not even close to the same level.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1169-1172)
    ka "「洸哉……{w=.3}也？{p} 对不起，我可不想和这家伙同一个等级」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3137
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_08ff00d4:

    # "As he says that, Kouya makes sure,{p}to cast a glare right at Torahiko."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1174-1174)
    "与此同时，洸哉看了看虎彦。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3138
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_44b26588:

    # to "「What are you...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1177-1178)
    to "「你说什么？……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3139
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_a5ce00fc:

    # "Sparks always fly when those two meet."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1180-1180)
    "他俩相遇总能擦出要打架的火花。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3140
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_a38ce19c:

    # to "「Hey Kouya.{p} You just splashed water at me on purpose,{p} didn't you?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1182-1183)
    to "「喂，洸哉。{p}你是不是故意把水溅到我身上的？！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3144
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_1e77bcdf:

    # ka "「That's right.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1185-1187)
    ka "「那又怎样？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3148
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_bc0efc37:

    # to "「That's right!?{p} Apologize, right now!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1189-1191)
    to "「怎么样？{p} 给我，{w=.3}立马过来！{p}道歉！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3152
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_348b2129:

    # ka "「Hmph, I'm just speaking on behalf,{p} of [fn]'s thoughts.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1193-1195)
    ka "「噗，我只是帮[fn]表达一下心情而已」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3153
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_48dbadf8:

    # "What, me?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1197-1197)
    "诶？我？"

# game/day 7.rpy:3154
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_9a372882:

    # "I wish I could have splashed him or something,{p}but I didn't think about that..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1199-1200)
    "倒是没想过要泼水之类什么的。 ……"

# game/day 7.rpy:3155
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_a74eccfe:

    # to "「Why are you dragging [fn] into this!?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1203-1204)
    to "「这跟[fn]有什么关系啊？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3156
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_f2962dfb:

    # ka "「Didn't you take off and leave [fn] alone?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1206-1208)
    ka "「你不是光顾着自己去冲浪， 而把[fn]扔下不管了吗？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3160
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_7d3ee253:

    # to "「I-I planned that to be an example...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1210-1212)
    to "「那，那只是我给他做的示范……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3161
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_97b1c86d:

    # ka "「[fn]'s still a beginner,{p} who doesn't know his left from right,{p} isn't he?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1214-1216)
    ka "「[fn]现在还只是一个连左右都分不清的初学者啊。{p} 那么一直陪在他身边，让他远离危险不是理所应当的吗？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3162
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_fd1d800f:

    # ka "You should always stay with him,{p} keeping him away from danger.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1218-1222)
    ka "「在你离开的那段时间里面， 如果[fn]出了什么事情， 怎么办？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3163
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_9f2c4b55:

    # ka "「What if something happened to him,{p} while you were away?{p} What would you have done?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1218-1222)
    ka "「在你离开的那段时间里面， 如果[fn]出了什么事情， 怎么办？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3164
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_c2864e6d:

    # "Wow... that's a pretty solid argument."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1224-1224)
    "呜哇……确实说的没错。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3168
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_3d1678e9:

    # to "「Ugh...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1239-1240)
    to "「呃……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3169
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_433b32a4:

    # to "「B-but he stood up on that wave,{p} so there wasn't any problem in the end!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1230-1232)
    to "「但，但他也不是在浪上站起来了吗？ 到最后也没出什么问题嘛」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3173
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_2e588f2c:

    # ka "「Regarless of the outcome,{p} that would have been a serious incident,{p} had [fn] been injured..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1234-1237)
    ka "「无论结果怎么样，如果[fn]因此受伤的话，你的责任就太大了！{p} 首先你要先对他道歉，不是吗？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3174
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_c6d1eed0:

    # ka "How about you give him an apology?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1236-1237)
    ka "「无论结果怎么样，如果[fn]因此受伤的话，你的责任就太大了！{p} 首先你要先对他道歉，不是吗？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3175
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_2075482a:

    # to "「Guh...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1240-1240)
    to "「呃……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3176
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_264c3ce0:

    # "With that said, Torahiko falls silent."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1242-1242)
    "被洸哉那么一说，虎彦沉默了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3177
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_fa926053:

    # "Usually when those two fight,{p}each of their claims develop,{p}like parallel lines."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1244-1246)
    "平时他们俩吵起来的时候， 因为双方的主张都保持着平行线， 无论是谁先发火的，只要有人来调解下就OK了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3178
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_5b0fdb77:

    # "Then when things get too hot,{p}somebody arbitrates so it's okay."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1246-1246)
    "无论是谁先发火的，只要有人来调解下就OK了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3179
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_3f0fbc0c:

    # "However, I feel that Torahiko is at a...{p}disadvantage this time."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1248-1248)
    "不过这次，我觉得虎彦处于下风。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3180
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_bc2b9bad:

    # "Being left alone in the water,{p}certainly did make me nervous."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1249)
    "被单独留在海里，确实让我感到很害怕。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3181
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_f04cf986:

    # "And being carried away by that wave,{p}really could have drowned me..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1250-1250)
    "而且被刚刚那浪冲着，确实有可能会溺死。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3182
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_80304b5d:

    # "But I don't mind.{p}I don't think I even want him to apologize."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1252-1253)
    "但是我不介意， 我甚至没有想过要虎彦给我道歉。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3183
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_cac962fc:

    # "I simply have no idea what I should do,{p}about this uneasy atmosphere."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1254-1254)
    "我真的不知道在这尴尬的气氛下该干嘛。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3184
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_ef89bd1f:

    # "There's nothing that he needs to apologize about.{p}Kouya wouldn't allow me to say that, thought."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1256-1257)
    "假如说其实也没必要道歉。{p} 估计洸哉也不会放过的。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3185
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_c7e338ed:

    # "Now I'm not the 3rd party of this argument,{p}and I'm not standing in the line,{p}of opposition. It's a delicate position."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1259-1261)
    "我现在既不是这场争论的第三者， 也无立场提出反对的意见， 真是个微妙的处境啊。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3186
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_ee7d89b1:

    # "This is troubling... What should I do?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1263-1263)
    "有点麻烦啊，现在该做些什么？"

# game/day 7.rpy:3190
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_7ae377f0:

    # ka "「Why are you so quiet?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1265-1267)
    ka "「你怎么不说话了？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3191
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_c24e3185:

    # to "「...Shut up.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1269-1271)
    to "「……闭嘴！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3192
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_96e988a5:

    # "Because of that argument,{p}Torahiko can't come up with a retort."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1273-1274)
    "因为被说的那些话是对的，虎彦想不出什么话来反驳， 显然，他也不愿照着洸哉的命令去做，"

# game/day 7.rpy:3193
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_a0a2057d:

    # "Nevertheless, he obviously can't stomach,{p}the idea of doing what Kouya,{p}ordered him to do."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1274)
    "显然，他也不愿照着洸哉的命令去做。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3194
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_4a36690c:

    # "He makes a stern facial expression,{p}from the strain of his stubborness."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1275-1275)
    "他一直露出极其不满的表情。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3198
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_7993c539:

    # ka "「Psh, you don't even know,{p} what [fn]'s thinking."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1277-1280)
    ka "「哼，你根本就连[fn]的想法都不知道， 亏你还能这样目中无人地呆着」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3199
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_06c7a230:

    # ka "How dare you shamelessly,\n be his coach like that.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1279-1280)
    ka "「哼，你根本就连[fn]的想法都不知道， 亏你还能这样目中无人地呆着」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3200
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_79e2c40b:

    # "Laughing through his nose,{p}and leaning his head forward,{p}he provokes Torahiko."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1282-1284)
    "洸哉也真是的。 哼哼地笑了几下，并把头倾向一侧，向虎彦挑衅。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3201
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_2831da3d:

    # "The atmosphere is starting to get tense,{p}I feel more and more unpleasant..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1286-1288)
    "周围的气氛一下子紧张起来了。 感觉有种不好的预感……{p} 在这种一触即发的状态下，突然打起来都不奇怪。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3202
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_ce870284:

    # "It wouldn't be strange if this...{p}touchy situation broke out into a scuffle..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1288-1288)
    "在这种一触即发的状态下，突然打起来都不奇怪。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3203
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_dcb250d2:

    # fn "「Forget it, why are you two fighting?{p} It's true I was a little scared,{p} but I don't care anymore.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1290-1293)
    fn "「好了好了，你们俩有啥好吵的？{p} 被一个人丢在那的时候确实有点害怕， 但是我没有特别在意的啦」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3204
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_e3d10345:

    # "Both of them look taken aback,{p}when they realize what I said."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1295-1297)
    "听到我说的话，他们两个都好像发现了什么似的看了过来。{p} 两个人一直横眉怒视对方， 好像把我还在场的事都忘掉了一样。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3205
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_3b991557:

    # "Together, they both glare at me.{p}It seems like they've already forgotten."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1296-1297)
    "两个人一直横眉怒视对方， 好像把我还在场的事都忘掉了一样。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3206
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_4ea178bc:

    # fn "「Kouya, you said too much.{p} Since we went through all this,{p} to have a good time"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1299-1302)
    fn "「洸哉也真是的，你有点说过了。{p} 难得一起出来玩， 再好好相处一点吧……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3207
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_b5cbad89:

    # fn "Let's try to get along a bit better...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1302-1302)
    fn "「再好好相处一点吧……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3211
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_4e3f9e89:

    # ka "「[fn]...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1305-1306)
    ka "「[fn]……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3212
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_19805c79:

    # to "「...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1309-1310)
    to "「……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3213
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_e4060e22:

    # fn "「Well then, I'm going for a swim.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1312-1313)
    fn "「那，我游泳去喽」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3217
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_e1c99f2c:

    # "I say no more and raise my hand,{p}with my back turned to both of them."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1315-1317)
    "我转过身背对着沉默的两个人，手稍稍向上一挥。 然后就抱起板子飞奔大海。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3218
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_3f148c14:

    # "I then carry my board,{p}and get into the water."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1317-1317)
    "然后就抱起板子飞奔大海。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3219
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_d3961c00:

    # "Somehow, in the flow of adolescent-like drama,{p}it's better to swim out to the open sea.{p}Just don't remind me of not being able to surf."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1319-1321)
    "……像青春电视剧的固有桥段那样，{p} 虽然游到了海浪这边， 但是，我好像忘记自己不会冲浪了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3220
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_1e81b0c5:

    # "I wonder why I tried to look good like that...{p}Oh well, it's already too late to turn back."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1323-1324)
    "我逞什么强啊，简直作死啊……{p} 算了，想回也回不去了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3221
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_ecca1beb:

    # ka "「[fn], it's stupid for a beginner,{p} to go riding alone.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1326-1327)
    ka "「[fn]，初学者一个人去冲浪也太乱来了吧」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3222
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_9ff743a6:

    # fn "「Oh, Ko-Kouya...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1329-1330)
    fn "「哦，{w=.3}洸，{w=.3}洸哉……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3223
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_385aa9c2:

    # to "「Yo, have you been caught by the...{p} charm of surfing or something?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1332-1334)
    to "「哟！ 果然有被冲浪的魅力吸引了吧？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3224
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_1b5a1fe6:

    # fn "「And Torahiko too...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1336-1337)
    fn "「虎彦你也……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3225
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_f9794541:

    # "They talk as if nothing had happened,{p}and greet me like they usually would,{p}giving a small embarrassed laugh."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1339-1341)
    "他们说着好像什么都没发生， 和平时一样的样子。 而且带着点害羞的笑。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3226
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_c5ad1368:

    # to "「This time I'll give you a proper take-off,{p} and be a reliable teacher!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1343-1345)
    to "「那现在就好好教教你， 正确的冲浪方式！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3227
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_6e3b4d07:

    # ka "「First, you should practice,{p} with the white caps near the shore."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1347-1349)
    ka "「首先还是先在岸边利用白浪练习下比较好。{p} 不用太勉强，慢慢来」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3228
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_8b3adb19:

    # ka "Don't force yourself too much,{p} and steadily step up.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1348-1349)
    ka "「首先还是先在岸边利用白浪练习下比较好。{p} 不用太勉强，慢慢来」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3229
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_55c62629:

    # fn "「All right, hehehe.{p} I wonder if I can do this right.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1351-1353)
    fn "「明白！嘿嘿。{p} 不知道我能不能学好？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3230
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_931610c5:

    # to "「You'll be fine!{p} Just work your way up!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1355-1356)
    to "「没问题！{p} 可以的，可以的！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3231
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_edfe235c:

    # ka "「That's my line.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1358-1359)
    ka "「那是我的台词」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3232
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_dec28f60:

    # to "「Shut up!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1361-1362)
    to "「你烦不烦？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3233
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_82d8eb4b:

    # fn "「Hey hey, are you fighting again?{p} ...Jeez.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1364-1365)
    fn "「喂喂，又要吵起来吗?{p} ……真没办法」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3234
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_f09a0de6:

    # "From then on I get lectured,{p}by both Torahiko and Kouya."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1367-1368)
    "于是，我就跟着虎彦和洸哉学习， 进步虽然不是很快。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3235
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_4bbef68d:

    # "Though my progress isn't rapid,{p}I am now able to stand on the board."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1368-1369)
    "进步虽然不是很快。 总之，在板子上站起来还是可以了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3236
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_a2130575:

    # "A little while after,{p}I get to the point,{p}when I can ride a wave."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1371-1372)
    "不一会儿，当我终于可以随着波浪前行的时候， 他们两个，也包括我，都很开心。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3237
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_aedef855:

    # "Both of them,{p}along with myself,{p}were quite pleased."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1372-1372)
    "他们两个，也包括我，都很开心。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3238
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_a18918da:

    # "Unconsciously, they decide,{p}to cross their arms,{p}and strike a triumphant pose,"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1374-1375)
    "两人无意识把手臂搂在了一起，摆了一个胜利的姿势， 然后瞬间分开，并尴尬地红着脸互相背了过去。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3239
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_eb88b80c:

    # "Then quickly, they turn their faces,{p}away in embarrassment,{p}and try to laugh it off."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1375-1375)
    "然后瞬间分开，并尴尬地红着脸互相背了过去。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3240
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_0f9ded01:

    # "It seems those two still have something...{p}similar to a good relationship."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1378-1378)
    "果然这两个人，关系还是不错的嘛。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3246
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_4353c9c3:

    # "When we return to the shore at noon,{p}my body is pleasantly exhausted."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1383-1384)
    "当我们中午上岸的时候， 身体都被舒适的充实感打得筋疲力尽了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3250
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_24a54fa5:

    # ka "「We sure did play a lot.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1387-1388)
    ka "「玩得真痛快啊！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3254
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_5b41319c:

    # to "「Heh heh, I actually wanted to get out,{p} into the higher waves,{p} but today was pretty fun!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1390-1393)
    to "「嘿嘿，本来还想去更高的浪上去耍耍的， 今天真的是玩得好开心！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3255
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_e6233b4f:

    # fn "「Both of you can be so energetic.{p} I couldn't move another step.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1395-1397)
    fn "「你们两个，好有精力啊。{p} 我是一步都走不动了」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3256
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_0be1d440:

    # to "「You're so slobby...{p} A man's body is his capital.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1399-1401)
    to "「真没出息啊～{p}男人的身体就是资本啊！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3257
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_5665037d:

    # "Torahiko bangs on my shoulders,{p}laughing loudly."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1403-1404)
    "虎彦啪啪地拍着我的肩膀，大笑道。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3261
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_5b79d2bf:

    # ka "「You really were riding out there,{p} seeing you look so excited was amusing.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1406-1409)
    ka "「确实你的冲浪技术十分豪爽， 而且看起来还很有趣的」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3265
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_3e948922:

    # to "「Humph, it's rare for you to compliment me,{p} isn't it? Even if you did make me,{p} do something like swallow sea water?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1411-1414)
    to "「洸哉竟然夸奖我了，真稀奇呀{p} 在海里面是不是不小心喝到了奇怪的东西啊」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3269
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_39b438cc:

    # ka "「D-don't get the wrong idea...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1416-1418)
    ka "「别，别想偏了！……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3270
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_a092dcfc:

    # ka "「The way you just force yourself,{p} through anything is just funny, is all!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1420-1421)
    ka "「我是想说不管什么都用力气使劲推，太搞笑了！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3274
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_d52b2810:

    # to "「Y-you're joking right?{p} Why am I embarrassed...{p} Jeez what a creepy feeling.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1423-1426)
    to "「我，我是在开玩笑的啊！{p} 害什么臊啊……{p} 真是的，令人不舒服的家伙！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3275
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_da595fc9:

    # to "「I-if that's the case... Then your...{p} surfing technique is pretty impressive.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1428-1431)
    to "「不，{w=.3}不过……{p} 洸哉你的冲浪技术也挺厉害的嘛」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3279
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_5f3ff643:

    # ka "「R-really...?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1433-1435)
    ka "「是，{w=.3}是吗…………」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3280
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_d49c1780:

    # to "「Y-yeah...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1437-1439)
    to "「嗯，{w=.3}嗯…………」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3281
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_fc5cfba7:

    # "This is a strange sight."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1441-1441)
    "真是奇怪的场面啊。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3282
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_96ebb5fa:

    # "Just a little bit ago they were fighting,{p}and now they're complimenting each other."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1443-1444)
    "刚刚明明还在吵架的， 现在却在相互褒奖。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3283
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_c9e0836d:

    # fn "「Kouya and Torahiko,{p} I can't tell if your relationship,{p} is good or bad.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1446-1447)
    fn "「洸哉和虎彦的关系，真是不知道是好是坏?」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3288
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_05dae08f:

    # to "「K-Kouya and I getting along?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1453-1455)
    to "「啊？我和洸哉的关系很好？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3289
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_8c5f580b:

    # ka "「Don't say something so...{p} disgusting!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1457-1458)
    ka "「不要说恶心的话了！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3290
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_4793b258:

    # fn "「There's no need for you two,{p} to be so serious..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1460-1462)
    fn "「两，两位，别那么认真嘛……{p} 不过，比刚才那样的打起来要好点」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3291
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_fd2bbb71:

    # fn "It's just the way you looked there,{p} was much better than...{p} when you're fighting.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1462-1462)
    fn "「不过，比刚才那样的打起来要好点」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3295
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_685e1a2e:

    # to "「Ooh...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1465-1466)
    to "「呜……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3299
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_4f2aeadc:

    # ka "「Hmm...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1469-1470)
    ka "「呃……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3300
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_096648e4:

    # "Oops, just when they were starting to forget,{p}I accidentally said something to remind them."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1472-1473)
    "糟了，好不容易让他们忘了的， 我又不小心说了让他们想起来的话了吗！？"

# game/day 7.rpy:3301
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_03743521:

    # "I go silent again,{p}and an air of akwardness flows in."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1475-1476)
    "又陷入了沉默中， 周围流动着紧张的气息。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3302
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_67d9c131:

    # to "「Y-you know what...?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1478-1480)
    to "「那，{w=.3}那个啥……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3303
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_4dc928c8:

    # "Breaking the atmosphere,{p}Torahiko timidly speaks up."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1481-1483)
    "虎彦小心翼翼地搭起了话， 打破了这种气氛。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3304
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_4e43adf0:

    # to "「About earlier... I'm sorry.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1485-1487)
    to "「那个，刚刚的事情，对不起」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3305
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_db2cb2c3:

    # fn "「It's all right, I don't mind.{p} It's kind of my own fault, anyway...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1489-1491)
    fn "「好了，我已经不介意了。{p} 某种程度上，我也有错……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3306
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_cc224151:

    # to "「Heh heh, that's okay."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1493-1496)
    to "「嘿嘿，你也没什么错！{p} 如果你还想去冲浪的话， 那我就安心了」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3307
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_b7d89142:

    # to "But, you felt a little better,{p} when you continued surfing, right?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1495-1496)
    to "「如果你还想去冲浪的话， 那我就安心了」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3311
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_11e409bc:

    # to "「Also...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1498-1500)
    to "「而且……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3312
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_c26badf6:

    # "Torahiko glances over at Kouya and mutters."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1502-1502)
    "虎彦眼角扫了下洸哉，嘟囔着。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3313
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_16f410f1:

    # to "「What Kouya said certainly wasn't wrong...{p} I was also a little too stubborn."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1504-1506)
    to "「确实，洸哉说的也没错的……{p} 是我有点固执。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3314
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_1868598a:

    # to "But spraying water at me...{p} was unacceptable!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1506-1507)
    to "「是我有点固执。 {p} 但是把水溅到我身上的事情不能原谅！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3315
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_21a8a032:

    # to "「Eh, what I'm... In other words,{p} I'm at fault here too."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1509-1512)
    to "「呃，那个，总之……{p} 我那时候也错了。 加上泼我水的事，我们就五五分吧」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3316
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_0f3a6d99:

    # to "So when you factor it all in,{p} it makes it about 50-50!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1512-1512)
    to "「加上泼我水的事，我们就五五分吧」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3320
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_c613afe9:

    # to "「So...!{p} I guess you could say...{p} {nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1514-1516)
    to "「怎么说呢……{p}那个，{p}这个，」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3322
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_2a779550:

    # extend "...my bad.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1516-1517)
    extend "「怎么说呢……{p}那个，{p}这个，{p} ……对不起」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3323
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_3ea0fcc9:

    # "Compared to my time,{p}that apology took...{p}some time to come out."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1519-1520)
    "跟和我道歉时相比， 抱歉这两个字出来的时间有点久啊。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3327
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_f848371d:

    # ka "「I also went farther than needed.{p} I'll honestly apologize for the water.{p} ...Sorry.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1522-1526)
    ka "「我也有点言重了。{p} 溅你水的事真心向你道歉。{p} ……对不起」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3328
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_f0f162f6:

    # "To be honest, I also got hit,{p}by that water pretty good too,{p}but..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1528-1529)
    "说实话，那水其实也有溅到我的身上的。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3329
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_7b95cc23:

    # "If I were to say that now,{p}I'd surely be recognized,{p}as the guy who can't read people's moods."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1531-1532)
    "但是 ，如果我现在那么说的话， 肯定会被认定为这个夏天最不会察言观色的家伙。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3330
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_13b9afb1:

    # fn "「So then, I'd say we resolved this.{p} So is this talk is over...?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1534-1536)
    fn "「那么，事情解决？{p} 那好，这个话题结束了以后不许再提」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3331
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_9e19cc4e:

    # to "「That's right!{p} If we hang around this any longer,{p} we'll never move on!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1538-1542)
    to "「好嘞！{p} 如果我们再在这方面上纠结的话， 我们只能止步不前的啊。{p} 让我们打起精神来吧」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3332
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_0eced8e6:

    # to "Let's cheer up!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1541-1542)
    to "「我们只能止步不前的啊。{p} 让我们打起精神来吧」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3336
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_148f4f22:

    # ka "「You change just as fast as ever...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1544-1546)
    ka "「你还是老样子，变得真快……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3340
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_639a8ba5:

    # to "「A cool guy doesn't stick in the past!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1548-1550)
    to "「好男儿从来不纠结过去发生的事情！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3341
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_c2c1792e:

    # ka "「Jeez...{p} {nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1552-1553)
    ka "「真是的……{p}反正最后[fn]也玩得很开心，」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3343
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_afbbb032:

    # extend "Well, if [fn]'s pleased with the result,{p} then it was worth it for us to teach him.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1553-1554)
    extend "「真是的……{p}反正最后[fn]也玩得很开心， 看来我们的指导没有白费」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3344
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_fcbcac49:

    # fn "「But I'm still a beginner compared to you two.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1556-1557)
    fn "「嘛～相对你们来说，我还只是个初学者嘛」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3345
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_abd5b923:

    # to "「You're so modest.{p} I think you we're able to understand a lot,{p} considering it's for your first time.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1559-1562)
    to "「别那么谦虚啦。{p} 作为第一次，已经相当了不起了」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3346
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_2eba8ca1:

    # fn "「Really?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1564-1565)
    fn "「真的？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3347
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_4f871064:

    # to "「Definitely! In fact...{p} The Torahiko Association of Surfing,{p} officially recognizes you as..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1567-1570)
    to "「千真万确！{p} 怎么说………… 经过虎彦冲浪协会官方正式认证， 你已经达到了5级的水平！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3348
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_ec89f71e:

    # to "...About 5th grade level!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1570-1570)
    to "「你已经达到了5级的水平！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3349
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_e8f84f40:

    # fn "「...I'll gratefully accept that.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1572-1573)
    fn "「……十分荣幸的接受这个称号！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3350
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_05a4cea9:

    # "After all, I did pretty well...{p}For my first time, at least."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1575-1576)
    "总而言之，虽然是第一次， 但作为实力来说似乎有些微妙。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3351
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_af14b695:

    # "However it seems doubtful I'll get,{p}to where I'm really good..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1576-1576)
    "但作为实力来说似乎有些微妙。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3352
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_f063f928:

    # to "「When you get better,{p} we should go tandem together!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1578-1580)
    to "「等你水平好点之后， 一起玩在一个板上双人冲浪！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3353
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_70cee56b:

    # fn "「T- tandem, huh...{p} That'd hurt, you'd be grinding up,{p} against my face!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1582-1584)
    fn "「什，{w=.3}什么双人冲浪啊……{p} 痛痛痛～！别碰我的脸！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3357
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_f19d3746:

    # ka "「Stop talking nonsense, Torahiko.{p} There's nobody here who's eager,{p} to take a ride with you.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1586-1589)
    ka "「别说蠢话了，虎彦。{p} 这儿没人希望和你一起冲浪」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3361
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_60f1e9d4:

    # to "「Really?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1591-1593)
    to "「你说什么！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3362
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_d9fd6a93:

    # fn "「Hey hey, stop.{p} You guys can fight,{p} when we get back to the village.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1595-1597)
    fn "「好了好了。{p} 你们要打回村之后再去打」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3366
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_b74053e0:

    # to "「All right.{p} When we get back to the village.{p} Remember that, Kouya.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1599-1602)
    to "「好，{p} 回去之后给我记着，洸哉」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3370
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_da526636:

    # ka "「Then let's do it.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1604-1606)
    ka "「谁怕谁啊」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3371
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_5ce362e5:

    # "Oh great, they reverted back,{p}to the way they usually are."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1608-1609)
    "好吧，又变回平时一样了，{p} 觉得这种关系不会有什么改善了……"

# game/day 7.rpy:3372
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_e9fea16c:

    # "Their relationship seems to have improved,{p}for the the time being..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1611-1611)
    "但是这样也还挺不错的。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3373
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_726109c4:

    # "But that's just the way things are."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1610-1611)
    "但是这样也还挺不错的。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3377
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_c396c247:

    # to "「I'm getting kind of hungry.{p} Let's go get some food.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1613-1616)
    to "「运动之后感到好饿啊。{p} 去吃点东西吧{w=.3」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3378
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_b5022eb3:

    # fn "「Sure.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1618-1619)
    fn "「嗯」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3379
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_ae56c3bd:

    # "Did we decide to go tandem together?{p}I don't really know what tandem means,{p}but I hope I can have fun with Torahiko again."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1621-1623)
    "一起双人冲浪吗？{p} 我真的不是很清楚双人冲浪都需要干些什么， 不过，又可以和虎彦他们一起玩了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3380
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_5e789264:

    # to "「What are you talking about?{p} Are you coming?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1625-1627)
    to "「你嘀咕什么呢?{p} 那是当然！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3381
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_b5ad05af_1:

    # fn "「Huh?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1629-1630)
    fn "「咦？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3385
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_0a76fc6a:

    # ka "「[fn], surfing is really fun.{p} Now that you've gotten a little better,{p} do you think you get it?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1632-1635)
    ka "「[fn]，从现在开始学的话， 冲浪的有趣之处，要上手以后才能知道的哦」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3386
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_60c054c6:

    # to "「Oh! Up next is Great Teacher Torahiko's,{p} swimming club training."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1637-1640)
    to "「喔！{p} 那么下次的话就是我虎彦大师的 斯巴达式游泳训练哟，做好觉悟吧！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3387
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_3fd08ae0:

    # to "So prepare for some really hard lessons!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1640-1640)
    to "「斯巴达式游泳训练哟，做好觉悟吧！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3388
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_82de06fc:

    # "Apparently, that's what he has,{p}in mind for me.{p}For now I'm going to eat, though."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1642-1643)
    "看样子，我心中想的事， 好像都从嘴里说了出来"

# game/day 7.rpy:3389
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_625674f0:

    # "I'll get to play with him again."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1645-1646)
    "对啊。 {p} 我还能和他们一起玩。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3390
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_6ede6a97:

    # fn "「All right, next I'm aiming,{p} to go from grade 5 to 2!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1648-1649)
    fn "「好，我下个目标是从5级升到2级！」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3393
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_64f8ac1c:

    # to "「What! Isn't grade 2...{p} a little too sudden?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1651-1653)
    to "「什么！{p} 到2级？ 那么突然」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3397
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_25e58dd3:

    # to "「Don't you think that's awfully hasty?{p} I'd even say that for grade 3.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1655-1658)
    to "「好像有点太快了吧？{p} 我也才3级而已啊」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3401
translate chinese_simplified beach07_torahiko_7d1ff936:

    # ka "「Torahiko, What is your standard for...{p} dividing grades, anyway...?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: torahiko/7日目.ks (KS 1660-1662)
    ka "「虎彦，你的级别到底以什么为基准的啊？……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3416
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_35c040cd:

    # fn "「Whew, I'm tired...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5388)
    fn "「呼～累死了……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3417
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_8cb18af3:

    # si "「Zzz, zzz...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5393)
    si "「ZZzz——，ZZZZzzz——」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3418
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_0ea8c16b:

    # to "「*Snore*, *snore*...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5398)
    to "「呼——呼——」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3419
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_f7bfd41f:

    # "Seems like everyone's asleep.{p}It's been so long since\nwe all went out together."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5400-5401)
    "看样子所有人都睡了啊。{p}好久没有大家一起出游了呢。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3420
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_be82fed2:

    # "And so long since, I've played so cheerfully."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5402)
    "我也玩得很开心啊。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3421
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_41134e8b:

    # ky "「Zzz, Sou... Want to try it?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5407)
    ky "「Zzz，宗……你要不要试一下……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3422
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_f5876c56:

    # so "「...Senpai...{p} for sure... *snore*...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5412-5413)
    so "「Zzz，前辈……{p}真的吗……呼呼——」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3423
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_d828d2ec:

    # "Hmhm, even in their dreams,\nthey're still playing."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5415)
    "哼哼，在梦里也在一起玩啊。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3424
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_b63e06b9:

    # ta "「Sa-Sachiko-san...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5420)
    ta "「幸、幸子……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3425
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_00ea3b67:

    # "Hm?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5422)
    "嗯？"

# game/day 7.rpy:3426
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_e90532eb:

    # ta "「Sachiko-san...{p} is the dashi for Father's meal done?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5425)
    ta "「幸子，{p}给父亲的下饭的汤好了吗？」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3427
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_cbe6ccd1:

    # ta "「There's also dust collecting on the window sill.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5426)
    ta "「窗台上也积了好多灰尘啊。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3428
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_9910de3f:

    # ta "「The meal preparations are far from done,{p} and I wonder if the cleaning is done well enough.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5429-5430)
    ta "「饭还没准备好呢，{p}清扫工作做得怎么样了……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3429
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_b941d2bd:

    # ta "「Guoooooh, *whistle*...{p} Like you said, people are truly...{p} *whistle*...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5433-5435)
    ta "「咕咕咕咕，{w=.3}咻——。{p}就像你说的，人们真的是……{p}咻——」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3430
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_e92e59b6:

    # "Seriously, who is Sachiko-san?{p}And what's more, did you change roles?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5437-5438)
    "说真的，谁是幸子？{p}而且，你是不是换角色了？"

# game/day 7.rpy:3431
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_12a2f759:

    # ky "「Hey Sou, how's this...?{p} You like it, don't you? Zzz...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5441-5442)
    ky "「喂，宗，这个怎么样？{p}你不是喜欢这个的吗？呼……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3432
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_101ea5c8:

    # so "「Aah, I can't...{p} I can't take that anymore...{p} *snore*...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5445-5446)
    so "「啊啊啊，{w=.3}我不能……{p}我已经不能再吃了……{p}呼呼呼」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3433
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_49cc9b41:

    # "Just what kind of dream are they having over there?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5448)
    "这边又是在做什么梦呢？"

# game/day 7.rpy:3434
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_63097753:

    # ka "「Zzz... Hey, isn't it all right?{p} Just for a little bit,\n nothing bad by doing it.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5455-5456)
    ka "「呼……嗯，{w=.3}行不行？{p}就一点点，\\n没坏处的……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3435
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_916d4035:

    # ko "「Zzz...{p} No [fn]... I...{p} Zzz...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5459-5460)
    ko "「呼……{p}不行啊，[fn]……我啊……{p}呼……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3436
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_dbababe0:

    # "And what are those two doing?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5462)
    "他们俩又在干嘛？"

# game/day 7.rpy:3437
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_88e17d02:

    # fn "「It's almost too good to be true,{p} especially on a day like this.{p} I wanted to go see everyone again.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5465-5466)
    fn "「美好得简直不像现实生活，{p}特别是在这样的一天。{p}想再看看大家呢。」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3438
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_e07693e2:

    # "Outside the window,{p}everything's being dyed red by the setting sun."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5468)
    "看着窗外，{p}一切都被夕阳染红了。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3439
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_c30a7add:

    # "The sea, the mountains, the sky,{p}everything's the color of orange juice."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5469-5470)
    "大海，青山，蓝天，{p}所有的一切似乎都是橙红的颜色。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3440
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_b34092ff:

    # "Somehow I feel like I'm the\nonly one who's been locked up,\non a different world."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5472-5473)
    "不知怎么的，\\n我觉得好像只有自己被关起来了，\\n在另一个不同的世界里……"

# game/day 7.rpy:3441
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_5a8525bb:

    # "...Something like that."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5474)
    "……这种感觉。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3442
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_ccbc2fc0:

    # fn "「*Yawn*... I'm sleepy...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5477)
    fn "「哈欠……唔，好困……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3443
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_74fdc93a:

    # "Since everyone else is sleeping,\nI'm starting to feel it it too.{p}But, I want to stay awake a bit more."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5479-5481)
    "大家都在睡觉呢，\\n我也觉得困了。{p}但是，我想保持清醒。"

# game/day 7.rpy:3444
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_eb6b97b4:

    # "We still haven't played enough.{p}I want to be with everyone."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5482-5483)
    "还没玩够呢。{p}还想和大家一起玩……"

# game/day 7.rpy:3445
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_16a3be1d:

    # fn "「Y-You think I'll sleep...{p} Sleep ...Zzz...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5486)
    fn "「我、{w=.3}才不会睡着呢……{p}睡着……呼……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3446
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_ce2e55ff:

    # to "「*Snore* *snore*.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5489)
    to "「呼……呼……」"

# game/day 7.rpy:3447
translate chinese_simplified beach07_ridehome_8526c5b8:

    # si "「Fufuu, there really is no helping you, is there...{p} Zzz, zzz...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: c_海水浴.ks (KS 5492-5493)
    si "「嗯嗯，真的拿你没办法呢……{p}呼……呼……」"

